hadiths[311]{hadithnumber,text}:
2477,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik dehati ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se hijrat ke mutalliq daryaft kya. (Madina munawwara mein sukunat ke liye baiat kerni chahi) aapney farmaya : ''tum par afsos! hijrat ka maamla intehai sakht hai, kya tumharey paas oont hain?'' usney kaha : haan. aapney puchha : ''unki Zakat detey ho?'' usney kaha : haan. aapney farmaya : ''un bastiyon ke paar amal kiye jao, Allah taala tumharey amal mein koi kami nahin kerega.''"
2478,"Miqdam bin Shureh apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke maine Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke basti aur dehat mein theharna kaisa hai? to unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (kabhi kabhar) un tilon aur maidanon ki taraf chaley jaya kartey they. aapney eik baar bahir janey ka irada farmaya aur meri taraf sadqa ke oonton mein se eik jawan oontni bheji (ke sawari ke doran mein us par kuch sakhti kerni padi) to aapney farmaya : ''Aaisha! naram khooi se kaam lo, narmi jis chiz mein bhi aa jaey wo muzayyan ho jati hai aur jis se nikal li jaey, wo aeb daar ho jati hai.''"
2479,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farmatey they : ''hijrat khatam nahin ho sakti, yahan tak ke tauba munqata ho jaey, aur tauba us waqt tak munqata nahin hogi, yahan tak ke Suraj maghrib se tulu ho.''"
2480,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke roz farmaya : '' (ab) hijrat nahin hai, lekin jihad aur niyat baqi hai, jab tumhen jihad ke liye dawat di jaey to nikal khadey ho.''"
2481,"Aamir (Shobi) ne kaha : eik shakhs Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaya jabke unke paas aur kuch log bhi mojud they, wo bhi unke paas beth gaya aur kaha : mujhey koi aisi baat bataeyn jo aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni ho to Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farmatey they : '' musalman '' wo hai jiski zaban aur haath se doosrey musalman mehfooz hun aur '' Muhajir '' wo hai jo Allah ke mana kiye huey kamon se baaz rahey .''"
2482,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farmatey they : '' hijrat ke baad hijrat hoti rahegi, zameen ke baasiyon mein sab se behtar wo log hongey jo Hazrat Ibrahim Alehissalaam ke daare-hijrat ko ikhtiyar kiye hongey. aur (qurbe-qiyamat ke waqt) burey log hi reh jaeyngey . unki zaminein unhen nikal bahir phenkengi, Allah azz-w-jall bhi unhen bura janega aur aag un logon ko bandaron aur khinziron ke sath jama karegi.''"
2483,"Hazrat (Abdullah) bin Hawala (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' halaat is tarah ho jaeyngey ke tum log mukhtalif girohon aur lashkaron mein jama ho jaogey, eik lashkar shaam mein hoga, eik Yamen mein aur eik Iraq mein.'' ibne-Hawala kehtey hain maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool! merey liye muntakhab farma dijiye, agar ye halaat paaun, to kahan sukunat ikhtiyar karun? aapney farmaya : ''Sham ko ikhtiyar kar lena, bila-shuba ye ilaaqa Allah azz-w-jall ka pasandida hai, Allah taala apney pasandida bandon ke yahin jama farma dega lekin agar tum log us se inkar karo, to phir apney Yamen ko ikhtiyar karna aur apney talabon ka pani pina, bila-shuba Allah taala ne mujhey shaam aur ahle-Sham ke mutalliq (fitnon se hifazat ki) zamanat di hai.''"
2484,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ka eik giroh hamesha haq ke liye qitaal karta rahega aur wo apney muqabil aaney walon par ghalib rahengey yahan tak ke unka aakhiri giroh Masih dajjaal se ladaai kerega .''"
2485,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya gaya ke mominon mein se kon sa aadmi kamil eman wala hai? aapney farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ki raah main apni jaan w maal se jihad karta ho, aur wo aadmi jo pahad ki kisi ghaati mein Allah ki ibadat mein mashghool ho aur logon ko uski burai na pahunchti ho.''"
2486,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya aur ijazat maangi ke mujhey sayahat ki ijazat marahmat farmaeyn, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba meri ummat ki sayahat jihad fi sabeelillah hai. ''"
2487,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jihad se wapas lotna (fazilat aur sawab mein) aisey hai jaisey jihad ke liye jana.''
2488,"Janab Abdul-Khabeer bin Sabit bin Qais bin Shamas apney walid sey, wo dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai jiska naam Umme- khallad tha, usney naqab dala hua tha, apney bete ke baarey mein sawal kar rahi thi jabkey wo (jihad mein) maara gaya tha. as-haabe-nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mein se kisi ne us se kaha : tum apney bete ke baarey mein sawal kerney aai ho aur naqab dal rakha hai. ( aisi pareshani mein pardey ka ye ehtimam?) usney kaha : agar mera beta kho gaya hai to maine apni haya to nahin khoi hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''terey bete ko do shaheedon ka sawab hai.'' usney puchha : ye kyon aey Allah ke Rasool? aapney farmaya : '' kyonkey usko ehle-kitab ne qatl kya hai. ''"
2489,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hajj, Umra ya jihad fi sabeel Allah ki gharz ke siwa samandari safar na kya jaey, bila-shuba samandar ke nichey aag hai aur aag ke nichey samandar hai.''"
2490,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke (meri khaala) Umme-Haram bint Milhan (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya aur ye ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida ( umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anha) ki behen hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( eik baar ( unke yahan qailula kya. aap jab bedaar huey to hans rahey they. kehti hain, maine puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool! aap kis baat par hans rahey hain? aapney farmaya : ''maine dekha ke (meri ummat mein sey) eik qom ke log (badi shaan sey) samandar mein safar kar rahey hain jaisey ke badshah takhton par hon.'' kehti hain : maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! dua farmaeyn ke Allah mujhey bhi un mein kar dey. aapney farmaya : ''tum bhi un mein se ho.'' aap phir so gaey aur jab bedaar huey to phir hans rahey they. maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! aap kis baat par hans rahey hain? to aapney pehley wali baat batai. maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! Allah se dua kijiye ke wo mujhey un logon mein se bana dey. aapney farmaya : ''tum pehley logon mein hogi.'' Anas bayan kartey hain ke baad mein Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se nikah kar liya aur jihad ke liye samandar ke safar par gaey aur un ( Umme-Haram ( ko bhi sath ley gaey aur jab wapis lotey to eik khachar unke liye laya gaya ke us par Sawar hun to usney unko gira diya, us se unki gardan toot gaee aur wo wafat pa gaeen."
2491,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab quba tashrif ley jatey, to Umme-Haram binte-Milhan (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan bhi jatey aur wo Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) ki zojiyat mein thin. aap eik din unke yahan tashrif ley gaey to unhoney aap ko khana pesh kya aur phir beth kar aap ke sar se juein talash kerney lagin. aur yehi mazkura hadees bayan ki. Abu-Dawud kehtey hain, binte-milhaan ki wafat qabras mein hui thi."
2492,"Hazrat umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anha) ki behen Ramisa se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) so gaey, phir jaagey jabkey ye apna sar dho rahi thin, aap jaagey to hans rahey they, usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! kya aap merey sar par hans rahey hain? aapney farmaya : '' nahin .'' aur puri hadees bayan ki jis mein kuch kami beshi hai. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : (Ramisa) umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anha) ki dudh-sharik behan hain aur yehi Umme-Haram binte-Milhan hain."
2493,"Hazrat Umme-Haram (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aapney farmaya : '' samandar ke safar mein jis ka sar chakraaey aur qai aa jaey to uskey liye eik Shahid ka sawab hai aur jo doob kar mar jaey usko do shaheedon ka sawab hai. ''"
2494,"Hazrat abu-Umama Bahli (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''teen (qism ke) aadmiyon ka Allah azz-w-jall zaamin hai : jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein jihad ke liye nikla tu Allah uska zaamin hai yahan tak ke (agar) uski wafat ho jaey to usko jannat mein dakhil kerega ya ajr w sawab aur ghanimat ke sath wapis lotaeyga, doosra wo aadmi jo masjid ki taraf gaya tu Allah uska zaamin hai yahan tak ke) agar ( uski wafat ho jaey to usko jannat mein dakhil kerega ya ajr w sawab aur ghanimat ke sath lotaeyga, aur teesra wo aadmi jo salam (ya salamti) ke sath apney ghar mein dakhil hua tu Allah azz-w-jall uska zaamin hai. ''"
2495,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kafir aur uska qatil (Mujahid) aag mein kabhi bhi ikhattey nahin ho saktey .''
2496,"Janab (Suleman) ibne-Barida apney walid (Barida (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghar par rehne waley logon par mujahideen ki aurton ki izzat w hurmat aisey ( wajib aur lazim ( hai jaisey ke unki apni maaeyn hon, jo koi (jihad sey) peechey rahey aur mujahideen ke gharwalon mein khayanat (bad-nazari ya khabaasat) ka maamla karey to qiyamat ke roz aisey shakhs ke liye jhanda lagaya jaeyga aur (usey ehle-mehshar mein ruswa kartey huey) Mujahid se kaha jaeyga : yehi shakhs hai jo terey peechey terey ehle mein burai karta raha, uski nekiyon mein se jo lena chahta hai, le-ley.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamari taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : ''to tumhara kya khayal hai?'' (bhala wo kuch chodega, yani hergiz nahin, sabhi nekiyan samet lega. Imam Abu-Dawud bayan kartey hain ke hadees key raawi Qaanab eik nek aadmi they, ibne-abi Leila ne unko qazi banana chaha to unhoney inkar kar diya aur kaha ke mujhey eik dirham ki koi maamuli chiz bhi leni hoti hai to doosrey aadmi ki madad leta hun ( to qaza w adaalat ki zimme daariyan kaisey utha sakta hun?) unhoney kaha : ham mein se kon hai jisey doosrey ki madad ki zarurat na padti ho? unhoney kaha : ab to ijazat den mein kuch soch lun. chunanche ijazat di gaee to chup gaey . Sufiyan bayan kartey hain ke usi keyfiyat mein they ke ghar ki chhat gir padi aur us se wafat pa gaey ."
2497,"iHazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo mujahideen Allah ki raah mein jihad ke liye nikaltey hain aur ghanimat hasil kar letey hain, wo apney aakhirat ke ajr mein se do tihai jald hi (us duniya hi mein) pa letey hain aur eik tihai unke liye baqi reh jata hai aur agar unhen koi ghanimat na miley to unka kamil ajr (qiyamat tak ke liye ( mehfooz ho jata hai. ''"
2498,"Janab Sehal bin Muaz apney walid ( Muaz bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raah mein jihad ke doran mein Namaz, rozey aur zikr ka ajr, Allah ki raah mein kharch kerney ke muqabley mein saat so guna tak badha diya jata hai.''"
2499,"Hazrat abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farmatey they : ''jo shakhs jihad ke liye rawana hua aur wafat pa gaya , ya qatl kar diya gaya , to wo Shahid hai, ya agar usko uskey ghodey ya oont ne gira diya ho, ya kisi janwer ne kaata ho, ya apney bistar hi par usey maut aai ho, ya jis kisi keyfiyat mein bhi uski wafat hui ho to wo Shahid hai aur bila-shuba uskey liye jannat hai.''"
2500,"Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her marney waley ka amal (uskey marney par) khatam ho jata hai, magar morcha band ke uska amal qiyamat tak ke liye badhta rehta hai aur wo qabr ke azab se (ya munkir-nakeer ke sawal jawab) se aman mein rehta hai. ''"
2501,"Hazrat Sehal bin Hanzala (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke (ham) log ghazwae Hunain ke moqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rawana huey aur bahut lambi masafat (doori) tey ki yahan tak ke pichhlaa pahar ho gaya. so mein Namaz ke waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan hazir tha ke eik ghud sawar aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main aap ke aagey aagey chalta raha yahan tak ke falan falan pahad par chadh gaya to dekha ke qabeelae Hawazin ke sab log apni aurton , chaupaaon aur bakriyon samet Hunain ki taraf jama ho rahey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne tabassum farmaya (muskuraen) aur kaha : ''kal inshaAllah ye sab musalmanon ki ghanimat hoga.'' phir farmaya : ''aaj raat kon hamara pehra dega?'' Hazrat Anas bin Abi Murtad Ghanwi (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main , aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney farmaya : ''to Sawar ho jao.'' chunanche wo apney ghodey par Sawar ho gaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya. aapney us se farmaya : ''us ghaati ki taraf chaley jao yahan tak ke uskey ooper chadh jao aur aisa na ho ke raat mein ham tumhari taraf se dhoka kha jaeyn.'' jab subh hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney musalley par tashrif laye aur do rakaten padhin. phir daryaft farmaya : ''kya tum ne apney sawar ko dekha hai? '' Sahaba ne kaha : nahin, aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham ne usko nahin dekha hai. phir Namaz ke liye takbir kahi gaee aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padhaaney lagey aur is dauran mein aap ghaati ki taraf bhi dekhtey rahey yahan tak ke jab Namaz mukammal kar li aur salam pher liya to farmaya : ''khushkhabri ho, tumhara sawar aa gaya hai.'' isliye ham bhi darakhton mein se ghaati ki taraf dekhney lagey, to wo samney aa gaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aa khada hua. usney salam kiya aur kaha : main (aap ke yahan sey) rawana hua yahan tak ke us ghaati ke ooper chadh gaya jahan Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm farmaya tha, jab subah hui to maine dono ghaatiyon mein dekha to mujhey koi shakhs nazar nahin aaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se puchha : ''kya tum raat ko (ghodey sey) utrey bhi they?'' usney kaha : nahin, sirf Namaz padhney ya qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se faraghat) ke liye hi utra hun. isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : ''tum ne apney liye lazim kar li (jannat) tum iskey baad aur koi amal na bhi karo to koi muwaakhiza (pooch-gachh) nahin.''"
2502,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs is haal mein mara ke usney jihad nahin kiya aur apney dil mein bhi jihad ki niyat nahin ki to wo nifaq ki eik shaakh par mara.''"
2503,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul (naqal hui) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney jihad mein hissey nahin liya , ya kisi Mujahid ko maaddi taawun (maali madad) nahin diya ya Mujahid ke rawana ho janey ke baad uskey ehle aur ayaal ki achchhi tarah khabargiri nahin ki tu Allah taala usey kisi musibat mein mubtala kar dega.'' Yazid bin Abdullah ne apni riwayat mein yun bayan kiya : ''qiyamat se pehley usey kisi musibat mein mubtala kar dega.''"
2504,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mushrekin se jihad karo : apney maalon ke sath , apni jaanon ke sath aur apni zabanon ke sath.''"
2505,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke sura tauba (ki aayat number 39) ''agar tum jihad ke liye na niklo gey tu Allah taala tumhen dard naak azab se dochaar kar dega.'' aur (aayaat :120 aur 121) ''Ehale Madina aur unke ird-gird ke dehatiyon ko munasib nahin (ke Allah ke Rasool se peechey rahen aur na ye ke apni jaanon ko Rasool ki jaan se piyari samjhen . ... .) in aayaat ko iskey baad wali aayat (number : 122) ne mansookh kar diya hai. jis mein hai : ''aur mominon ko layaq nahin ke ye sab ke sab jihad ke liye nikal khadey hon. (aisa kyon na hua ke her jamaat mein se eik giroh nikalta taake wo baqi deen mein samajh hasil kartey aur jab ye (jihad sey) laut kar aatey to apni qom ko bhi daratey taake wo bhi mutanabbeh (aagah) rahen).''
2506,"Najda bin Nafee kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se sura tauba (ki aayat : 39) ki tafseer poochhi, jis mein hai ke ''agar tum jihad ke liye na niklo gey tu Allah tumhen dard naak azab se dochaar kar dega.'' unhoney farmaya : un se barish rok li gaee aur yehi unka azab tha."
2507,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke pehlu mein baitha hua tha ke aap ko sakeenat ne dhanp liya (wahi ka nuzool shuru ho gaya) aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki raan meri raan par aa gaee, mujhey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki raan se jo bojh mehsoos hua kisi aur chiz se mehsoos nahin hua. jab aap se ye kaiyfiyat door hui to aapney farmaya : ''likho.'' chunanche maine shaaney ki haddi par likha : (* * *لا يستوي القاعدون) ( aakhir aayat tak ) ''Allah ki raah mein jihad kerney waley momineen aur baithe rehney waley barabar nahin ho saktey . ... .'' ibn Umme-Maktum jo na-bina sahabi they unhoney jab mujahideen ki ye fazilat suni to khadey huey aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! momineen mein se aisey shakhs ke baarey mein kya irshad hai jo jihad ki istataat na rakhta ho? unhoney jab apni baat puri ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sakeenat ne dhanp liya aur aap ki raan meri raan par aa gaee , aur dusri baar bhi maine isi tarah ka bojh mehsoos kiya jo pehley mehsoos kiya tha. phir jab aap se ye kaifiyat door hui to aapney farmaya : ''aey Zaid ! padho.'' maine padha : (لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين . .  ۔) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : (غير أولي الضرر) ''siwaye unke jinhen koi uzr ho.'' aur baqi aayat usi tarah rahi. Hazrat Zaid farmatey hain ke (غير أولي الضرر) ke lafz Allah ne alehda se nazil farmaai aur maine unko unki jagah par likh diya. qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! goya main shaaney ki haddi ke us darz ko dekh raha hun jahan maine usko milaayaa tha."
2508,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba tum log Madiney mein aisey logon ko chhod aaye ho, ke jo safar bhi tum kartey ho ya koi kharch kartey ho ya koi wadi tey kartey ho to wo (ajr aur sawab mein) tumharey sath hotey hain.'' Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! wo hamarey sath kis tarah hotey hain halanke wo Madiney mein hain? aapney farmaya : ''unko uzr aur majboori ne rokey rakha hai.''"
2509,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis kisi ne Mujahid ko samaane-jihad diya, to bila-shuba usney jihad kiya, aur jo Mujahid ke ehale-khana ki ba-husn aur khoobi (achchhi tarah) khabargiri karta raha, to bila-shuba usney jihad kiya.''"
2510,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne banu-Lahiyaan ki janib eik muhim bheji aur farmaya : ''har do aadmiyon mein se eik jihad ke liye chala jaey (aadhey log jihad ke liye jaeyn aur aadhey rukey rahen).'' phir aapney rukney walon se farmaya : ''jo tum mein se Mujahid ke ghar walon ki umda taur par khabargiri kerega usko janey waley ka aadha sawab hai.''
2511,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farmatey they : ''insan mein do wasf (khubi) bahut burey hotey hain : eik ye ke laalchi aur w bakheel honey ke sath sath dil ka kachchaa ho. doosra ye ke itna buzdil ho ke goya dil hi nikal jaeyga.''"
2512,"Janab Aslam Abu-Imraan bayan kartey hain ke ham log Madina Munawwara se jihad ke liye rawana huye, ham Qustuntuniya (istanbul) jana chahtey they aur Janab Abdur-Rehman bin Khalid bin Waleed hamarey ameere jamaat they. romi log apni pusht shehar ki faseel taraf kiye hamarey madde-muqaabil they. musalmanon mein se eik shakhs ne dushman par halla bol diya to logon ne kaha : rukoo , thehro ! (La-ilaaha-illallah) , ye shakhs apney aap ko halakat mein daalta hai to Hazrat Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ye aayat ham Ansariyon hi ke baarey mein nazil hui thi. jab jalaal wale Allah ne apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki nusrat farmaee aur Islam ko ghalib kar diya to ham ne kaha : chalo ab zara apney amwaal aur jaaidaad mein ruk jaeyn aur unko durust kar lein , tu Allah taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaee : ''aur Allah ki raah mein kharch karo aur apney aap ko halakat mein na dalo.'' halakat mein dalna ye tha ke ham apney maalon mein ruk jaeyn, unki islah mein mashghool ho jaeyn aur jihad chhod den. Abu-Imraan ne kaha : chunanche Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) Allah ki raah mein jihad kartey rahey, yahan tak ke Qustuntuniya (istanbul) hi mein dafn huey ."
2513,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''Shan wale Allah eik teer ki wajeh se teen aadmiyon ko jannat mein dakhil karta hai. eik uska bananey wala, jo apni us banaee hui cheez mein ajr aur sawab ka umeedwar ho. doosra , teer maarney wala (jihad mein) aur teesra wo jo usey teer pakdaaney wala ho (jo uska muawin (mazdoor) ho). teer-andazi aur ghod sawari seekho , taaham (phir bhi) mujhey ghud-sawari ki nisbat teer andazi (nishana bazi) ziyada pasand hai. (shariyat mein) khel teen hi hain : eik ye ke insan apney ghodey ko sadhaaey . doosra , ye ke insan apni biwi se kheley . teesra , ye ke insan apney teer kamaan se teer phainkney ki mashq karta rahey. jo shakhs teer andazi seekhney ke baad us se bezar ho kar usey chhod dey to usney bila-shuba eik nemat ko chhod diya.'' ya yun farmaya : ''usney is nemat ki nashukri ki.''"
2514,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member par chadh kar ye kehtey huey suna : (aapney sura Anfaal ki aayat : 60 padhi) ''in kuffar ke muqabley mein jis qadr ho sakey quwat baham pahunchao.'' (is ki tashreeh mein aapney farmaya :) ''khabrdar ! teer andazi hi quwat hai. khabrdar ! teer andazi hi quwat hai. khabrdar ! teer andazi hi quwat hai.''"
2515,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jihad do qism ka hai : jisney Allah ki raza chahi , Imam ki itaat ki, umda maal kharch kiya, apney shareek-kaar se narmi ka bartao kiya aur fasad se bachta raha, to bila-shuba aisey Mujahid ka sona aur jaagna sabhi ajr aur sawab ka kaam hai lekin jisney fakhr, dikhlaao aur shohrat ki niyat rakhi, Imam ki nafarmani ki aur zameen mein fasad kiya to bila-shuba aisa aadmi (sawab to kya) barabari ke sath bhi nahin palta.'' (gunah se bach aana bhi mushkil hai.)"
2516,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! eik insan jihad ke liye nikalta hai magar wo duniya ka maal chahta hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uskey liye koi ajr nahin.'' logon ne is farman ko bahut giraa'n jana, unhoney is aadmi se kaha : dobara poochho , shayad tum apni baat wazeh nahin kar sakey ho. usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! eik insan jihade fi-sabee-lillah (Allah ke raaste mein jihad) ke liye nikalta hai aur wo duniya ka maal chahta hai? aapney farmaya : ''uskey liye koi sawab nahin.'' logon ne is aadmi se kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se phir poochho. usney aap se teesri baar puchha to bhi aapney usey yehi farmaya : ''usko koi sawab nahin.''"
2517,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul (naqal hui hai) hai ke eik dehati Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : eik aadmi qitaal karta hai shohrat ke liye , koi qitaal karta hai tareef ke liye aur koi ghanimat ke liye aur koi martaba (bahaaduri aur shuja'at) dikhaney ke liye? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs is gharz se ladey ke Allah ka kalma buland ho to wohi Allah ki raah mein hai.''"
2518,Amr bin Murra ne kaha : maine Abu-Waeil se hadees suni jo mujhey bahut pasand aai . aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya.
2519,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke (maine kaha) aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey jihad aur ghazwey ke mutalliq irshad farmaeyn. aapney farmaya : ''aey Abdullah bin Amr ! agar tum sabr ke sath aur ajr ki niyat se qitaal karo tu Allah taala tumhen sabr kerney walon aur ajr ke talab gaaron mein uthaeyga aur agar tum dikhlawe aur maal jama kerney ki gharz se qitaal karo tu Allah taala tumhen riya kaar aur maal jama kerney walon mein uthaeyga , aey Abdullah bin Amr ! jis haal (aur niyat) mein bhi tum ne ladaai ki (jihad kiya) ya tumhen qatl kar diya gaya tu Allah tumhen usi haalat par uthaeyga.''"
2520,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tumharey bhai uhud mein Shahid kar diye gaey to Allah taala ne unki roohon ko sabz (hara) rang ke parindon mein kar diya jo jannat ki nehron par aatey hain, wahan ke phal khatey hain aur phir soney ki qindeelon mein laut jatey hain jo arsh ke saye mein latak rahi hain. jab unhoney wahan ke khaney peeney aur aaram aur rahat ke mazey dekhey to kaha : kon hai jo hamara ye paigham hamarey bhaiyon tak pahuncha dey ke ham jannat mein zinda hain, hamein rizq diya jata hai taake wo jihad se be-raghbat na ho jaeyn aur ladaai mein buzdili na dikhayen. chunanche Allah taala ne ye aayat nazil farma di: (wla تحسبن الذين قتلوا في سبيل الله أمواتا . ... .) ''wo log jo Allah ki raah mein qatl huey unke baarey mein ye khayal hergiz na kijiye ke wo murda hain balke wo zinda hain apney Rab ke paas rizq diye jatey hain.''"
2521,"Hasnaa binte Muawiya Sareemiya bayan karti hain ke ham se hamarey chacha (Aslam bin Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bayan kiya, unhoney kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya ke jannat mein kon hoga? aapney farmaya : ''nabi jannat mein hongey, Shaheed jannat mein jaeyga , chhota bachcha jannat mein jaeyga aur zinda dafn kiya gaya bachcha jannat mein jaeyga.''"
2522,"Janab Namraan bin Utba Zamaari bayan kartey hain ke ham Umme-Dardaa (Saghr) ke yahan gaey aur ham yateem they to unhoney kaha : tumhen bashaarat ho ! maine (apney shohar) Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Shahid ki sifarish apney gharaney ke sattar afrad ke haq mein qubul ki jaeygi. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke is sanad mein (Waleed bin Ribah Zimaari sahih nahin balke) Ribah bin Waleed sahih hai."
2523,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke jab Najashi (Rahimahullah) ki wafat hui to ham log kaha kartey they ke uski qabr par Noor dikhai deta hai. Abu-Saeed ne ham se kaha : Ahmed bin Abdul-Jabbaar ne hamein bayan kiya ke ham ko Yazid bin Buker ne ibne Is'haq se isi ki manind riwayat kiya.
2524,"Hazrat Ubaid bin Khalid Salma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do aadmiyon mein bhai chaaraa karaya tha. chunanche eik (jihad mein) qatl ho gaya aur uska doosra sathi eik hafte baad ya uskey qarib faut hua, ham ne uska janaza padha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''tum ne (iskey haq mein) kiya kaha hai? ''ham ne kaha : ham ne iskey liye dua ki aur kaha : aey Allah ! isko apney sathi ke sath mila dey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''to iski wo namaazen jo uskey baad padhta raha, wo rozey jo uskey baad rakhta raha aur wo amal jo uskey baad karta raha, kiya huey? unke darmiyan to itna fasla hai jaisey ke zameen aur aasman ke darmiyan.'' Shoba ko (في صومه) ke alfaz mein shak hua hai."
2525,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''an-qareeb tumharey liye badey-badey shehar Fateh kiye jaeyngey aur lashkar jama kiye jaeyngey, unke kuchh hissey tumharey zimmey aaeyngey (tumharey mukhtalif qabeelon aur ilaqon se log un mein shamil kiye jaeyngey). to (aisey bhi hoga ke) tum mein se koi us fauj mein baghair ujrat ke shamil hona pasand nahin kerega aur apni qom mein se nikal khada hoga aur qabeela qabeela ghoomtaa phirey ga , apney aap ko un par pesh kerega aur kahega : kon hai ke falan lashkar mein main uski (taraf se ujrat par ladtey huey) kifaayat karun? kon hai ke falan lashkar mein main uski taraf se (ujrat par) kifaayat karun? khabrdar ! aisa aadmi to mehaz mazdoor hai chahey (chaahe) apna aakhiri qatra khoon bhi baha dey.''"
2526,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jihad kerney waley ko apna sawab milta hai aur jo koi kisi Mujahid ko taawun deta hai usey apna sawab milta hai aur sath hi jihad kerney waley Mujahid ka bhi .'' (dugna sawab milta hai.)
2527,"Hazrat Yaala bin Muniya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jihad ka aelan farmaya jabkey main boodha aadmi tha, mera koi khaadim bhi na tha to mujhey kisi aisey mulaazim ki talash hui jo (jihad mein) meri kifaayat karta aur main usko iska hissey deta, chunanche mujhey eik aadmi mil gaya. phir jab kooch ka waqt hua to wo merey paas aaya aur kaha : mujhey nahin maloom ke (maale-ghanimat mein) hissey kya hongey aur mera hissey kitna hoga? isliye aap mujhey mutayyan (tei-shuda) taur par bata den wo aaye na aaye (mujhey us se gharz nahin.) to maine uskey liye teen Dinar mutayyan kar diye. phir jab main ghanimat leney ke liye hazir hua aur chaha ke uska hissey usey dun to mujhey muqarrar karda dinaaron ka khayal aaya. main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur us aadmi ka maamla aap ke samney pesh kiya. aapney farmaya : ''mein uskey is jihad mein duniya aur aakhirat mein siwaye in dinaaron ke jo usney muqarrar kar liye aur kuchh nahin paata.''"
2528,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : main aap ke paas hijrat par baiat ke liye hazir hua hun aur apney maa-baap ko rotey huey chhod kar aaya hun. aapney farmaya : ''unke paas ja aur unhen hansa (aur khush kar) jaisey ke to ne unko rulaayaa hai.''
2529,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main jihad karna chahta hun. aapney farmaya : ''kya terey maa baap hain?'' usney kaha : haan. aapney farmaya : '' to to unhi mein jihad kar (unki khidmat kar, yehi tera jihad hai.'') Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke sanade-hadees mein raawi Abul-Abbaas ye shayer hai aur iska naam Saaib bin Farukh hai."
2530,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke eik shakhs Yamen se hijrat karkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahuncha. aapney is se puchha .''kya Yamen mein tera koi aziz bhi hai? '' usney kaha : merey maa baap hain. aapney puchha : ''kya unhoney tujhey ijazat di hai? '' usney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''unke paas wapis ja aur un se ijazat talab kar. agar wo ijazat dey den to jihad kar warna unki khidmat kar.''
2531,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (meri walida) Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anha) aur ansaar ki kuchh aurton ko jihad mein sath ley jaya kartey they taake wo pani pilaen aur zakhmiyon ki marham patti karen.
2532,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen baaten emaan ki asal hain. jis shakhs ne (La-ilaah-illallah) ka iqrar kiya uskey dar-pai na ho, usey kisi gunah ki bina par kafir na kaho aur na kisi amal ki wajeh se usey emaan se nikalo. aur jab se Allah ne mujhey Nabi banakar bheja hai jihad jari hai aur jari rahega yahan tak ke is ummat ka aakhiri hissey dajjaal se qitaal kerega, usko kisi zalim ka zulm ya aadil ka adl (insaaf pasand ka insaaf) batil nahin kar sakta aur taqdeeron par emaan rakhna."
2533,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum par har ameer ke sath jihad wajib hai chahey (chaahe) nek ho ya bad, aur tum par har musalman ke peechhey Namaz padhna wajib hai chahey (chaahe) wo nek ho ya bad, agar-che bade gunaahon ka murtakib (mujrim) hi kyon na ho, aur tum par wajib hai ke her musalman ki Namaz (janaza) padho chahey koi nek ho ya bad , agar-che bade gunaahon ka murtakib (mujrim) ho.''"
2534,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kiya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jihad ka irada kiya aur farmaya : ''aey muhaajiro aur ansariyo ! tumharey kuchh bhai aisey bhi hain ke unke paas maal nahin aur na koi unka khuwesh (rishtedar) qabila hai to tum mein se her eik ko chahiye ke un mein se do teen aadmiyon ko apney sath mila ley, chunanche ham mein se jis kisi ke paas sawari thi wo apney sathi ko baari se sawar karta aur khud bhi baari se sawar hota tha.''Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : maine bhi do teen ko apney sath mila liya to mujhey apney hi oont par baari se sawari milti thi jaisey ke unhen."
2535,"Ibne-Zagab Ayaadi ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Hawala Azdi (Raziallahu anhu) merey mehman baney, to unhoney mujh se bayan kiya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ham ko paidal (jihad ke liye) rawana farmaya taake koi ghanimat hasil kar laeyn. isliye ham wapis aaye aur hamen koi ghanimat na mili. aapney mashaqqat aur ghami ke aasaar hamarey chehron par dekhay to khadey huey aur (dua kartey huey) farmaya : ''aey Allah ! unhen merey supurd na kar dey ke unki kifalat se aajiz rahun aur na unhen unki apni jaanon ke supurd kar dey ke apni kifalat se aajiz rahen aur na unhen logon ke supurd kar dena ke wo apney aap hi ko tarjeeh deney lagen. phir aapney apna haath Mubarak merey sar par rakha aur farmaya : ''aey ibne Hawala ! jab tum dekho ke khilaafat zameene-muqaddas (shaam) tak pahunch gaee hai to zalzaley aaney lagengey, museebatein tootengi. (iske alawa) aur bhi badi-badi alamaten zahir hongi aur qiyamat us waqt logon ke is se ziyada qarib hogi jitna ke mera haath tumharey sar par hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Abdullah bin Hawala (Raziallahu anhu) ka talluq hims se hai."
2536,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hamarey Rab taala ko us bandey par bada tajjub aata hai jo Allah ki raah mein jihad ke liye nikley, aur uskey sathi bhag niklen (magar) us bandey ko gunah ka ehsas ho to wo (qitaal ke liye) wapis laut aaye yahan tak ke uska khoon baha diya jaey, tu Allah taala apney farishton se kehta hai. dekho merey bandey ki taraf ke merey yahan sawab ki raghbat mein aur meri pakad ke dar se wapis laut aaya yahan tak ke uska khoon baha diya gaya.''"
2537,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke umr bin Aqeesh ne logon se Islam se pehley ka sood lena tha, to wo uski wasul-yaabi tak Islam se door raha. aakhir uhud ke din aaya aur puchha ke merey chacha zaad kahan hain logon ne kaha : uhud mein hain, phir puchha ke falan kahan hai? unhoney kaha : uhud mein hai. phir puchha ke falan kaha hai? unhoney kaha : uhud mein hai. chunanche usney apney hathiyar pehney , ghodey par Sawar hua aur un logon ki janib chala gaya. musalmanon ne jab usko dekha, to kaha : aey umr ! ham se door raho. usney kaha . yaqeen karo ke main emaan la chuka hun chunanche qitaal (jang) kerney laga yahan tak ke zakhmi ho gaya. usey isi haalat mein utha kar uskey ehle mein laya gaya isliye Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) iskey paas aaye aur uski behan se kaha : is se poochho (ke usney jang mein hissey kyon liya hai) apni qom ki hamiyat aur himayat mein, ya unke liye ghusse ki bina par, ya Allah ke liye ghussey ki wajeh se? to usney kaha : balke main Allah aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye ghussey ki wajeh se (is jang mein shareek hua hun). chunanche wo faut ho gaya aur jannat mein dakhil hua aur usney Allah ke liye eik bhi Namaz nahin padhi thi."
2538,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke khaibar ke moqe par merey bhai (Aamir bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu)) ne khoob qitaal (jang) kya aur (Allah ka karna aisa hua ke) uski apni talwaar chat kar khud usko lag gaee jis se wo qatl ho gaya. as-haabe-Rasul (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey baarey mein baaten kerney lagey aur us (ki shahadat) ke silsiley mein unhoney shak ka izhar kiya ke eik aadmi apney hi hathiyar se maara gaya hai (to kyonkar (kis tarah) Shahid samjha jaeyga?) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye jihad kartey huey faut hua aur Mujahid faut hua hai.'' ibne-Shahab Zohri kehtey hain ke phir maine Salma bin Akwa ke bete se puchha to usney mujhey apney baap ke hawaley se usi ki manind bayan kiya magar uskey alfaz ye they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghalat kehtey hain, ye jihad kartey huey faut hua hai, Mujahid faut hua hai aur iskey liye dugna ajr hai.''"
2539,"Janab Abu-Salaam Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke eik sahabi se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney bayan kiya ke ham ne juhaina ke eik qabiley par hamla kiya. isliye musalmanon mein se eik aadmi ne unke eik aadmi par waar kiya aur usey maarna chaha magar uska waar khata gaya aur uski talwaar khud usey hi lag gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey musalmano ! tumhara bhai ! (is ki khabar lo).'' log bhag kar uski taraf gaey to dekha ke wo faut ho chuka hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne isko usi ke kapdon mein khoon samet lapet diya, iski Namaze janaza padhi aur usey dafn kar diya. logon ne puchha . aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya wo Shahid hai? aapney farmaya : ''haan aur main iskey liye gawah hun.''"
2540,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do waqt ki duaen radd nahin ki jatin ya bahut kam radd ki jati hain : eik Azan ke waqt aur dusri jang ke waqt, jab log eik doosrey ke sath bhid jatey hain. Musa (bin Yaqoob) ne kaha : mujhey Rizq bin Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman ne Abu-Haazim sey, usney Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kiya : ''barish ke waqt (bhi dua radd nahin ki jati).''"
2541,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farmatey they : ''agar kisi ne oontni ko dobara dohney ke waqfe ke barabar bhi qitaal kiya (jang ki) to uskey liye jannat wajib hai, aur jisney Allah se sachchey dil se Allah ke raaste mein qatl ki dua maangi phir faut ho gaya ya qatl kar diya gaya to uskey liye Shahid ka sawab hai.'' ibne Masfee ne yahan izafa kiya : ''aur jisey (dushman ki taraf sey) Allah ki raah mein koi zakhm aa gaya ya koi chot lag gaee to qiyamat ke din wo zakhm isi tarah (taza) aur bada hoga jaisey ke wo tha, iskey khoon ka rang Zaafran ka aur khushbu kastoori ki hogi, aur jisey Allah ki raah mein koi phodaa nikal aaya to us par shaheedon ke jaisi mohar hogi.''"
2542,"Hazrat Utba bin Abd Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahey they : ''ghodon ki peshaniyon, gardanon aur dumon ke baal na kaato, bila-shuba unki dumeen unke pankhey hain (ke wo un se makkhiyon waghaira ko door kartey hain) aur gardanon ke baalon se ye apni sardi door kartey hain aur peshaniyon ke baalon ke sath khair aur barkat bandhi hui hai.''"
2543,"Hazrat Abu-Wahab Jushmi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aisey ghodey muntakhab kiya karo jo kamiyat aur paanch kaliyaan hon (rang surkh siyah ho magar peshani aur chaaron paon safed hon) ya ashqar paanch kaliyaan hon (rang surkh ho aur peshani aur chaaron paon safed hon) ya mushki (siyah rang) aur paanch kaliyaan hon.''"
2544,"Hazrat Abu-Wahab ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghodaa aisa muntakhab karo jo ashkar paanch kaliyaan hon (surkh rang) ya kamiyat safed peshani.'' aur mazkura hadees ki manind zikr kiya. Muhammad bin Muhajir kehtey hain : maine apney shaikh se puchha ke ashqar ko fazilat kyon hai? to unhoney kaha : kyonkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik muhim bheji to jo shakhs sab se pehley Fateh ki khushkhabri lekar aaya wo ashqar ghodey par Sawar tha."
2545,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghodon mein barkat unke surkh rang walon mein hai.''"
2546,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mada ghodi ko ''fars'' kaha kartey they.
2547,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) shikaal qism ke ghodon ko napasand farmatey they. aur shikaal se murad ye hai ke uskey daain paon aur baeyn haath mein safedi ho ya daain haath aur baeyn paon mein safedi ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne wazahat ki ke haath paon mein safedi mukhalif jati ho.
2548,"Hazrat Sehal bin Hanzala (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik oont ke paas se guzrey jis ka pet uski kamar se lag gaya tha to aapney farmaya : ''in be-zaban janwaron ke baarey mein Allah se daro, in par sawari karo to bhaley andaz mein aur khilao to bhi umda tarah se.''"
2549,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey apney sath sawari par peechhey bitha liya aur khamoshi se mujhey eik baat batai jo main kisi ko bhi nahin bataun ga, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko qazaey-hajat ke liye chupney ki do jaghen bahut ziyada pasand thin. ya to koi oonchi jagah hoti, ya koi khajuron ka jhund hota . aap eik baar eik Ansari ke baagh mein tashrif ley gaey to wahan eik oont tha, jab usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha to roni si aawaz nikali aur uski aakhon se aansu bahney lagey, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey paas aaye aur uskey sar par haath phera to wo chup ho gaya. phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''is oont ka Malik kon hai? ye kis ka oont hai? '' to eik Ansari jawan aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye mera hai. aapney farmaya : ''kya to is janwar ke baarey mein Allah se nahin darta jis ka usney tujh ko Malik banaya hai, usney mujh se shikayat ki hai ke to usey bhookaa rakhta aur bahut thakaata hai.''"
2550,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik aadmi kisi raastey mein ja raha tha ke usey bahut piyas lagi, usey eik kunwaan mila, wo is mein utra , pani piya aur bahir nikla to usney eik kutta dekha jo haanp raha tha aur piyas ki wajeh se geeli mitti chaat raha tha is aadmi ne socha ke us kuttey ko bhi piyas ne sataya hai jaisey ke mujhey sataya tha. isliye wo dobara kunwen mein utra , apney mozey ko pani se bhar kar apney munh se pakda aur ooper chadha aur kuttey ko pilaya, so Allah taala ne uska ye amal qubul farma liya aur usey bakhsh diya.'' Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya hamarey liye janwaron ki khidmat mein bhi sawab hai? aapney farmaya : ''har geeley jigar (jaan daar) mein sawab hai.''"
2551,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke ham jab kisi manzil par utartey to us waqt tak Namaz na padhtey they jab tak ke oonton par se kajawey na utaar letey.
2552,"Hazrat Abu-Basheer Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke wo eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they. ... ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik paighamber bheja , raawi hadees Abdullah bin Ubai Bakr ka kehna hai : mera khayal hai ke shaikh ne bayan kiya : log raat ki aaram-gaah mein they (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kehla bheja ke) ''kisi oont ke galey mein koi rassi ya koi qalada baqi na chhoda jaey magar usey kaat dala jaey. Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : mera khayal hai, bad-nazari se bachao ke liye ye daltey they."
2553,"Sahibe Rasool Hazrat Abu-Wahab Jushmi (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghodon ko baandh kar rakho (unki khoob dekh bhaal karo) unki peshaniyon aur sirinon (pushton) par haath phera karo.'' raawi ko shak hai ke aapney lafz ''(أعجازها)'' kaha ya ''(أكفالها)'' aur gardanon mein rassiyan baandho magar taant ki rassi na ho.''"
2554,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis qafile aur jamaat mein ghanti ho, farishtey uskey sath nahin hotey.''"
2555,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''farishtey us jamaat ke sath nahin chaltey jinkey sath kutta ho ya ghanti.''"
2556,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghanti ke mutalliq farmaya : ''ye shaitan ka baajaa hai.''
2557,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, farmaya aisey janwar par sawari kerney se mana kiya gaya hai jo gandagi khata ho."
2558,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisey oont ki sawari se mana farmaya jo gandagi khata ho."
2559,Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eik gadhey par aap ke peechhey baitha hua tha jisey ufair kaha jata tha.
2560,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Amma-Baad : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey sawaron ko , jab ham ghabraatey to (خيل الله) ''Allah ke shehsawaar bando ! , keh kar pukartey , aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein hukm detey they ke jab khof aur ghabrahat ki kaifiyat ho to ikhattey ho jaya karen, sabr aur sukoon se kaam lein aur aisey hi qitaal (jang) ke waqt kiya karen."
2561,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul (naqal hui hai) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik safar mein they, isliye aapney (kisi sey) lanat kerney ki aawaz suni to aapney puchha : ''ye kya hai?'' Sahaba ne kaha : ye falan aurat hai jisney apni sawari ko lanat ki hai. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us se (kajaawa aur saman) utaar do. bila-shuba ye ab fitkaara hua hai.'' chunanche Sahaba ne us se (saman waghera) utaar diya. Imran kehtey hain : goya main uski taraf dekh raha hun ke wo siyahi maael oontni thi."
2562,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya hai ke janwaron ko aapas mein ladaya jaey.
2563,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke merey bhai (Abdullah bin Abi Talha) ki wiladat hui to main usey lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua taake aap usey ghati den. maine aap ko bakriyon ke baadey mein paya, aap bakriyon ko nishan laga rahey they. (Shoba ne) kaha mera khayal hai, shaikh ne bayan kiya : aap unke kanon par nishan laga rahey they."
2564,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se eik gadhaa ley jaya gaya jiskey chehrey par dagh diya gaya tha to aapney farmaya : ''kya tumhen ye baat nahin pahunchi ke maine aisey shakhs par lanat ki hai jo kisi janwer ko uskey chehrey par daaghe ya uskey munh par maarey?'' chunanche aapney is kaam se mana farma diya.
2565,Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik khachchar hadiya diya gaya to aap us par Sawar huey. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar ham gadhon ko ghodiyon par chadhaaen (to unke is jinsi amal sey) hamen is tarah ke khachchar hasil ho jaeyngey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahil log ye kaam kartey hain.''
2566,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab safar se tashrif latey to hamarey sath aap ka istaqbal kiya jata to jis (bachchey) ke sath aap ka pehley istaqbal kiya jata aap usey apney aagey bitha letey. chunanche merey sath aap ka istaqbal kiya gaya to aapney mujhey apney aagey bitha liya phir Hazrat Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) aaye ya Husain (Raziallahu anhu) to aapney unko apney peechhey bitha liya, phir ham Madiney mein dakhil huey to isi tarah they (ke teeno eik sawari par Sawar they)."
2567,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney janwaron ki peethon ko member bananey se bacho, bila-shuba Shan Wale Allah ne unko tumharey tabey kiya hai taake tumhen eik shehar se doosrey shehar tak pahuncha den jahan tum nafson ki mashaqqat ke baghair pahunch hi nahin saktey they aur usney tumharey liye zameen banai hai to apni zarooraten is par puri kiya karo.''"
2568,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shaitanon ke oont hotey hain aur shaitanon ke ghar bhi, shaitanon ke oont maine dekhay hain, tum main eik apney sath khoobsurat oontniyaan lekar chalta hai unhen khoob mota taza kiya hota hai khud kisi par Sawar nahin hota, apney kisi bhai ke paas se guzarta hai jo chalney se aajiz hua tha, usey bhi sawar nahin karta aur shaitan ke ghar maine nahin dekhey hain. '' Janab Saeed bin Abi Hind kaha kartey they : main samajhta hun ke shaitan ke ghar yehi haudey aur kajawey hain jin ko logon ne reshmi kapdon se dhanpa hota hai."
2569,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum shadab ilaqon mein safar karo to oonton ko unka haq diya karo (ke wo bhi kha aur char lein) aur jab khushki ke (din ya ilaqey hon) to jaldi jaldi chala karo (taake sawaariyon ko aziyat na ho) aur jab tum raat ko aaram ke liye kahin padaaw karo to raastey se hatt kar padaaw kiya karo.''"
2570,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura hadees ke misl (jaisi) bayan kartey hain. is riwayat mein (حقها) ke baad ye izafa hai ke ''(maroof) manaazil (aur masafat) se tajawuz mat kiya karo (aage mat nikla karo).''
2571,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''raat ke pehley pahar (ya raat ko bhi) safar kiya karo, bila-shuba raat ke waqt zameen lapet li jati hai."
2572,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif liye ja rahey they ke eik shakhs aaya aur uskey paas gadhaa tha, usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! (aaiye !) Sawar ho jaiye aur wo khud peechhey ko ho gaya. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, tum apni sawari par aagey baithney ke ziyada haq daar ho. siwaye iskey ke tum apna ye haq mujhey dey do.'' usney kaha : be-shak main apna ye haq aap ko deta hun, so aap Sawar ho gaey."
2573,"Ibad bin Abdullah bin Zuber apney razaai (doodh shareek) baap se riwayat kartey hain jo ke bani Murra mein se they aur ghazwae-mautaa mein shareek huey they. kehtey hain : qasam Allah ki ! main goya Hazrat Jaafar bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekh raha hun ke wo apney surkh ghodey se utar padey, uski koonchen kaat dalin, phir kafiron se ladtey rahey yahan tak ke khud qatl ho gaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye hadees qawi nahin hai."
2574,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''muqabla sirf teen chizon mein jayez hai oont daud,  ghud daud ya teer andazi.''"
2575,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne muzmir ghodon mein muqabla karwaya aur unke liye hafiya se saneyyatal-wadaa tak ka fasla muqarrar tha, aur ghair muzmir ghodon mein muqabla karwaya to unke liye saneyyatal-wadaa se masjid bani zuraiq tak ka fasla muqarrar tha, aur Abdullah in muqabla kerney walon mein shareek they aur kamiyab rahey they."
2576,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul (naqal hui hai) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghodon ko muzmir banaya kartey , jin mein muqabley kiraaey jatey they."
2577,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghud daud ka muqabla karaya to jo ghodey paanchwen saal mein dakhil ho chukey they, unke liye daud ka fasla ziyada rakha tha."
2578,"Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main eik safar mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath thi , maine aap ke sath daud mein muqabla kiya to main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se aagey badh gaee. phir jab main bhari ho gaee to aap mujh se badh gaey. to aapney farmaya : '' (ye us (pehli daud) ka badla hai.''"
2579,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney do (muqabla kerney waley) ghodon mein (apna) ghoda dakhil kiya aur uskey jeet janey ka yaqeen na ho to ye jua nahin hai, aur jisney un mein apna ghoda dakhil kiya jabkey usey yaqeen ho ke ye jeet jaeyga to ye jua hai.''"
2580,"Hazrat Zohri (Rahimahullah) ne ba-sanad Ibad bin Awam bayan kiya aur mazkura baala ke ham-maani zikr kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is riwayat ko Maamer, Shuaib aur Aqeel ne Zohri ke wastey kaee ulama se naqal kiya hai aur ye hamarey nazdik sahih tar hai."
2581,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''na (جلب) hai aur na (جنب)'' Yahya bin Half ki riwayat mein saraahat hai yani ''muqabley mein''."
2582,Hazrat Qatada (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke (جلب) aur (جنب) muqable-bazi mein hota hai.
2583,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki talwaar ke qabze ki topi chaandi ki thi.
2584,Saeed bin Abi Hasan (Rahimahullah) ki riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki talwaar ke qabza ki topi chaandi ki thi. Qatada kehtey hain : mujhey maloom nahin ke kisi ne uski mutaabiat (pairwi) ki ho.
2585,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se mazkura baala hadees ki manind marwi (bayan) hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : in sab mein Saeed bin Abi Hasan (Rahimahullah) ki riwayat qawi hai aur baqi zaeef hain.
2586,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik shakhs ko hukm diya jo masjid mein teeron ko sadqa taqseem kerney ja raha tha ke wo jab un teeron ko lekar chaley to unko phalon ki taraf se pakdey .
2587,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi hamari masjid ya baazar mein se guzrey aur uskey paas teer hon to chahiye ke unhen unke phalon ki taraf se pakad kar rakhey.'' ya farmaya : ''unhen apni mutthi se pakdey rahey'' ya farmaya : ''unhen apni mutthi se pakdey rahey ke kahin kisi musalman ko na lag jaeyn.''"
2588,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai : beshak Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke talwaar ko is kaifiyat mein liya diya jaey ke wo nangi ho (miyaan mein na ho).
2589,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, be-shak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai ke chamdey ke tukdey ko do ungliyon ke darmiyan rakh kar kaataa jaey."
2590,Janab Saaib bin Yazid (Rahimahullah) ne eik shakhs se riwayat ki aur uska naam bhi bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uhud ke din ooper taley do zirhen pahni hui thi.
2591,Hazrat Muhammad bin Qasim (Rahimahullah) ne apney ghulam ko Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein bheja ke wo un se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke alam ke mutalliq poochh kar aaye ke wo kaisa tha? to unhoney bataya ke wo kalay lakeer daar ooni kapdey ka aur chokor tha.
2592,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mutalliq bataya ke jis din aap makkey mein dakhil huye, us din aap ka jhandaa safed rang ka tha."
2593,"Hazrat Samaak bin Harab apni qom ke eik aadmi sey, aur wo eik doosrey se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka alam dekha jo zard rang ka tha."
2594,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''merey liye saufaa aur kamzor logon ko talash karo, tum log apney kamzor logon hi ke zariey se rizq diye jatey aur madad kiye jatey ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya ke raawi hadees Zaid bin Irtaat, Adi bin Irtaat ke bhai hain."
2595,Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke (eik jang mein) muhajrin ka shiaar ''Abdullah'' aur ansaar ka ''Abdur-Rehman'' tha.
2596,"Hazrat Ayas bin Salma apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath mein jihad kiya to hamara shiaar tha (أمت أمت) (maani hai maar dey, maar dey aur is mein kuffar ki hazeemat aur musalmanon ki Fateh ka tafaul tha)."
2597,"Hazrat Mohllab bin Abi Sufra ka kehna hai ke mujhey us shakhs ne bayan kiya jisney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna tha, aapney farmaya : ''agar tum par raat ko hamla ho jaey to tumhara shiaar (حم لا ينصرون) hona chahiye .''"
2598,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab safar par rawana hotey to ye dua padhtey they : (اللهم ! أنت الصاحب في السفر ، والخليفة في الأهل ، اللهم ! إني أعوذبك من وعثاء السفر وكآبة المنقلب وسوء المنظر في الأهل والمال ، اللهم ! اطولنا الأرض وهون علينا السفر) ''aey Allah ! safar mein to hi hamara rafeeq aur ehle mein khalifa hai. (unki hifazat kerney wala hai) aey Allah ! safar ki mashaqqat aur shiddat se main teri panah chahta hun aur is baat se ke gham aur andoh ke sath wapis lautoon aur apney ehle aur maal mein koi bura manzar dekhun, aey Allah ! hamarey liye zameen ko lapet dey aur safar ko hamarey liye aasan farma dey.''"
2599,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Janab Ali Al Azdee ko safar ke aadaab mein ye sikhaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi safar ki gharz se apney oont par baith jatey to teen dafa kehtey (الله اكبر) phir kehtey :(سبحان الذي سخر لنا هذا وما كنا له مقرنين ، وإنا إلى ربنا لمنقلبون . اللهم ! إني أسألك في سفرنا هذا البر والتقوى ، ومن العمل ما ترضى ، اللهم ! هون علينا سفرنا هذا ، اللهم ! اطولنا البعد ، اللهم ! أنت الصاحب في السفر والخليفة في الأهل والمال) ''paak hai wo zaat jisney is sawari ko hamarey tabey kiya, ham (khud se) isko apna tabey na bana saktey they aur bila-shuba ham apney Rab hi ki taraf laut janey waley hain. aey Allah ! main tujh se apney is safar mein neki aur taqwe ka sawal karta hun aur aisey amal ki tofiq chahta hun jo tera pasandida ho, aey Allah ! hamarey liye hamara ye safar aasan farma dey aur masafat ko hamarey liye lapet dey, aey Allah ! safar mein to hi rafeeq aur ehle aur maal mein khalifa hai.'' aur jab wapis tashrif latey to yehi kalmaat padhtey aur in mein ye izafa kartey : (آيبون تائبون عابدون لربنا حامدون) ''ham wapis aaney waley hain, tauba kerney waley hain, apney Rab ki ibadat kerney waley aur uski hamd kerney waley hain.'' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke lashkari jab kisi ghaati par chadhtey to (الله اكبر) aur agar kisi pasti mein utartey to (Subhan-Allah) kehtey aur Namaz bhi isi qaaedey par hai) ke uthtey baithtey takbir kahi jati hai)."
2600,"Hazrat Qaz'aa kehtey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne mujh se kaha : idhar aao ! main tumhen wadaa kahun , jaisey ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wadaa kaha tha : (أستودع الله دينك وأمانتك وخواتيم عملك) ''main terey deen , teri amanat aur terey amal ke ikhtitaam ko Allah taala ke hawaley karta hun.''"
2601,"Hazrat Abdullah Khitmi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi lashkar ko wadaa kehna chahtey to yun farmatey : (أستودع الله دينكم وأمانتكم وخواتيم أعمالكم) ''main tumhara deen , tumhari amanaten aur tumharey aamaal ka ikhtitaam Allah taala ke supurd karta hun.''"
2602,"Janab Ali bin Rabeea kehtey hain ke main Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan hazir tha ke sawar honey ke liye aap ke samney sawari laee gaee. aapney jab apna paon rikaab mein dal liya to kaha : (بسم الله) phir jab theek tarah se us par baith gaey to kaha : (الحمد الله) phir kaha : (سبحان الذي سخر لنا هذا وما كنا له مقرنين وإنا إلى ربنا لمنقلبون ) ''paak hai wo zaat jisney isko hamarey tabey kiya aur ham khud se isko apna tabey na bana saktey they aur bila-shuba ham apney Rab hi ki taraf laut janey waley hain.'' phir kaha : (الحمد الله) teen baar. phir kaha : (الله اكبر) teen baar. phir kaha : (سبحانك إني ظلمت نفسي فاغفرلي ، انه لا يغفر الذنوب إلا أنت) ''aey Allah ! to paak hai maine apni jaan par zulm kiya hai to mujhey maaf farma dey, bila-shuba terey siwa aur koi nahin jo gunahon ko bakhsh sakey.'' phir aap hansey. aap se kaha gaya : ameerul-momeneen ! aap kis baat par hansey hain? farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha tha ke aapney aisey hi kiya tha jaisey ke maine kiya hai aur aap hansey (bhi) they, to maine aap se puchha tha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap kis baat par hansey hain? aapney farmaya : ''bila-shuba terey Rab ko apney bandey par tajjub aata hai jab wo kehta hai (Ilaahi !) merey gunah bakhsh dey, banda janta hai ke merey siwa gunahon ko koi bakhsh nahin sakta.''"
2603,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab safar kartey aur raat aa jati to kehtey : (يا أرض ! ربي و ربك الله ، أعوذبالله من شرك وشر ما فيك و شرما خلق فيك ومن شرما يدب عليك ، وأعوذ بالله من أسد وأسود ، ومن الحية والعقرب ومن ساكن البلد ومن والد وما ولد) ''aey zameen ! mera aur tera Rab Allah hi hai. main Allah ki panah chahta hun terey shar sey, aur us shar se jo terey andar hai aur jo terey andar paida kiya gaya hai aur har us chiz ke shar se jo tujh par chalti phirti hai. main Allah ki panah chahta hun sher sey, kalay naag se aur saanp aur bichho se aur is ilaqey ke rehney walon ke shar sey, aur jan-ne waley ke shar se aur jis ko wo janey uskey shar se .''"
2604,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Suraj ghuroob hotey hi apney chopayon ko mat chhodo, yahan tak ke raat ka andhera khoob chha jaey, bila-shuba jis waqt Suraj ghuroob hota hai shayateen fasad kartey hain, yahan tak ke raat ka andhera chha jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke (الفواشي) se murad her qism ki ghoomney phirney wali chizen hain."
2605,"Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney kaha : bahut kam aisey hota ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jumerat ke alawa kisi aur din safar ke liye nikaltey."
2606,"Hazrat Sakhr Ghaamidi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! meri ummat ke liye inki subhon mein barkat dal dey.'' chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko koi muhim ya lashkar rawana karna hota to unhen din ke pehley pahar rawana farmatey. aur Hazrat Sakhr (Raziallahu anhu) eik tajir sahabi they, to wo apney karindon ko din ke pehley pahar rawana kiya kartey they, chunanche wo maal daar ho gaey they aur unka maal khoob badh gaya tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : unka naam Sakhr bin Wdaa'a hai."
2607,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid (Shoaib) se aur wo (Shoaib) apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''akela Sawaar eik shaitan hai, do Sawaar do shaitan hain aur teen Sawaar eik qafila hain.''"
2608,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab teen afrad safar par niklen to chahiye ke eik ko apna ameer muqarrar kar len.''"
2609,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab teen afrad safar mein hon to chahiye ke eik ko apna ameer bana len.'' Naafe (Rahimahullah) (maula ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma)) ne kaha : (ye hadees sunney ke baad) ham ne Abu-Salma (bin Abdur-Rehman bin Auf) se kaha : aap hamarey ameer hain."
2610,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai ke insan Quran majeed lekar dushman ke ilaqey mein jaey. Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain, mera khayal hai is nahi ki hikmat ye hai ke kahin ye dushman (kafir) ke haath na lag jaey (aur wo iski hatak karey)."
2611,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' behtareen rufaqaa (dost) wo hain jo chaar ki tadaad mein hon aur behtareen dasta wo hai jis mein chaar so shehsawaar hon aur behtareen lashkar wo hai jo chaar hazar ki tadaad mein ho aur baara hazar qillat ki bina par hergiz maghloob (parajit) nahin ho saktey.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : sahih ye hai ke ye riwayat mursal hai."
2612,"Hazrat Sulaiman bin Barida apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ( kisi shakhs ko) kisi dastey ya kisi badey lashkar ka ameer bana kar rawana kartey to usey khud apni zaat mein Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar kerney aur apni ma'iiyat mein doosrey musalmanon ke sath bhalai kerney ki wasiyat kartey aur farmatey : ''jab tum apney mushrik dushman ke muqabley par aao to unhen teen baaton ki dawat do , wo jisey bhi ikhtiyar karna chahen kar lein aur phir jo wo ikhtiyar kar lein usey qubul kar lena aur apney haath ko un se rok lena. (1) ( sab se pehley ( unhen Islam ki dawat dena , agar wo isey qubul kar lein to tum bhi un se qubul kar lo aur un se apney haath rok lo . phir unhen dawat do ke wo apna ilaaqa chhod kar daarul-muhaajiriin mein muntaqil ho jaeyn aur unhen batao ke agar unhoney ye baat qubul kar li to unko wohi huqooq hasil hongey jo muhajrin ko hasil hain aur un par wo sab kuchh wajib hoga jo un muhajrin par wajib hai, agar wo muntaqil hona qubul na keren aur apney ilaqon hi mein rehna chahen , to unhen batana ke wo badwi musalmanon ki tarah hongey, un par Allah ka hukm usi tarah nafiz (laagu) hoga jaisey ke deegar momineen par nafiz hota hai, ( maal ( fai aur ghanimat mein unka koi hissey na hoga , siwaye iskey ke musalmanon ke sath jihad mein shareek hon. (2) isliye agar wo log Islam qubul kerney se inkari hon to unhen kehna ke jiziya dena qubul keren agar wo is par razi ho jaeyn to usey qubul kar lena aur apna haath un se rok lena. (3) agar wo jiziya deney par razi na hon tu Allah ki madad talab kartey huey un se qitaal (jang) karna. aur jab tum kisi qiley walon ka muhaasra kar lo aur phir wo tum se ye chahen ke unko hathiyar dalney do , us shart par ke un par Allah ka hukm nafiz ho to ye baat qubul na karna kyonkey tum nahin jantey ke unke baarey mein Allah ka faisla kya hai, lekin unhen apni sharton aur faisley ke mutabiq hathiyar dalney ki ijazat do aur phir jo chaho unke mutalliq faisla karo . Sufiyan bin Uena kehtey hain ke Alqama ne kaha : maine ye hadees Muqaatil bin Hayyaan se zikr ki to unhoney kaha : mujhey Muslim ne bayan kiya.  Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : us ( muslim) se murad Muslim bin Haisam hai. usney Nauman bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kiya jaisey ke Sulaiman bin Barida ne bayan kiya hai."
2613,"Hazrat Sulaiman bin Barida apney walid se bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke naam se aur Allah ki raah mein ghazwa karo aur Allah ka inkar kerney walon se qitaal (jang) karo . ghazwa karo ghadr na karo, ( ghanimat mein) khayanat na karo, maqtooleen (qatal hue logon) ke ang na kaato aur na kisi bachchey ko qatl karo.''"
2614,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chalo Allah ke naam sey, Allah ki madad hasil kartey huey aur Rasulullah ki millat par qaaim rehtey huey (aur uski dawat detey huey ( , kisi buddhe khoosat ko qatl na karna , na kisi bachchey ya naabaaligh ko aur na kisi aurat ko .) ghanimat mein) khayanat se baaz rehna , ghanimat ke maal ko jama rakhna aur islah (sudhar) ka maamla karna , neki aur ehsan apnaana , bila-shuba Allah taala ehsan kerney walon se mohabbat karta hai.''"
2615,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne buwera ke maqam par qabeela bano nazeer ki khajuren jalaai thin aur kaati bhi thin, is par Allah taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaai : (ما قطعتم من لينة . . ۔) ''jo khajuren tum ne kaat dalin ya jadon par qaaim rehney deen so wo Allah ke hukm se tha, aur taake Allah taala faasiqon ko ruswa kar dey.''"
2616,Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya tha ke ''ubnaa'' ke ilaqey par subah ke waqt chadhai karna aur usey jala dena.
2617,"Abdullah bin Amr Gazzi kehtey hain ke maine Abu-Mushir se suna, un sey, ''ubnaa'' ke mutalliq puchha gaya to unhoney kaha : ham uskey mutalliq khoob jantey hain ke ye Palestine mein ''ubnaa'' ke naam se maroof (mash-hoor) jagah hai."
2618,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( waqia Badr se pehley ( Busaisa ko bataur jaasoos rawana farmaya tha ke wo dekhay ke Abu-Sufiyaan ka qafila kis marhalay mein hai?
2619,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi ( daurane safar mein) janwaron ke paas se guzrey aur un mein unka Malik mojud ho to us se ijazat ley , agar wo ijazat dey dey , to doodh doh ley aur pi ley , agar Malik mojud na ho to teen baar aawaz lagaey , agar wo jawab dey to us se ijazat talab karey warna doodh nikal ley aur pi ley magar sath na ley jaey.''"
2620,"Hazrat Ibad bin Shurehbil ka bayan hai ke mujhey qehat (akaal) (aur bhook) ne sataya , to main Madina ke eik baagh mein chala gaya aur wahan se maine eik baali li , usey masla aur kha liya aur kuchh apney kapdey mein bhi baandh ley chala , isliye baagh ka Malik aa gaya to usney mujhey maara aur mera kapda bhi chheen liya. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aa gaya to aapney us se farmaya : '' to ne isey samjhaya nahin jabkey ye nadan tha aur na to ne isko khilaya jabkey ye bhookaa tha.'' ( lafz ( جائعا ( bola ya ( ساغبا ( maani eik hi hai) phir aapney usko hukm diya, to usney mera kapda wapis kar diya aur mujhey eik wasq ya aadha wasq tuaam (khana) bhi diya."
2621,Abu-Bashar riwayat kartey hain ke maine Ibad bin Shurehbil se suna jo hamarey qabeela bani ghabar mein se they. aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat ki .
2622,"Hazrat Raafe bin Amr Ghifaari ka bayan hai ke maine ladakpan mein Ansariyon ki khajuron ko) pathar waghaira ( maara karta tha to mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya. aapney puchha : ''aey ladkey ! to khajuron ko kyon maarta hai?'' maine kaha : phal khaney ke liye. aapney farmaya : ''mat maara kar, jo nichey giri padi ho kha liya kar.'' phir aapney merey sar par haath phera aur dua di : ''aey Allah ! iskey pet ko sair kar dey .''"
2623,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi kisi ke janwar ka baghair ijazat doodh na nikaley, kya tum pasand kartey ho ke koi uski kothhri ( store ( ko tod kar uska zakhira tuaam (khaane ka zakheera) nikal ley jaey ? (aisey hi) janwaron ke than apney malikon ke liye doodh jama kartey hain to koi kisi ke janwar ka doodh na nikaley magar ye ke Malik ki ijazat ho."
2624,"Ibne-Juraij (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke) aayat kareema ) (يأيها الذين آمنوا أطيعوا الله وأطيعوا الرسول وأولي الأمر منكم ) ''aey emaan walo ! Allah ki itaat karo, Rasool ki itaat karo aur apney un logon ki jomamlat mein ikhtiyar rakhte hon.'' Hazrat Abdullah bin Qais bin Adi (Raziallahu anhu) ke baarey mein nazil hui thi , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko eik muhim mein bheja tha. ( ibne-Juraij kehtey hain (ke mujhey ye riwayat Yaala ne ba-waaste Saeed bin Jubair Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se bayan ki. ( tafseer nichey likhi riwayat mein hai)"
2625,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik lashkar rawana farmaya aur un par eik shakhs ( Abdullah bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu)) ko ameer banaya aur in ( lashkar walon ( ko hukm diya ke ameer ki baat sunen aur uski itaat karen, to usney aag bhadkai aur unhen hukm diya ke is mein kood jaeyn to eik qom ne uski ye baat manney se inkar kar diya aur kehney lagey ke ham aag hi se to bhagey hain ( musalman huey hain (aur kuchh doosrey logon ne aag mein kood janey ka irada kiya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye khabar pahunchi to aapney farmaya : ''agar ye is mein dakhil ho jatey to phir hamesha usi mein rehtey.'' aur farmaya : ''Allah ki nafarmani mein koi itaat nahin, itaat hamesha neki ke kamon mein hai.''"
2626,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalman par wajib hai ke) tamam ehkam ( suney aur maaney , chahey usey pasand ayen ya napasand hon, jab tak usey nafarmani ka hukm na diya jaey, jab gunah ka hukm diya jaey to na sunna hai aur na itaat hai."
2627,"Hazrat Aqba bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai. ... jo ke Bishr bin Aasim ki qom se they. ... . unhoney bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik muhim bheji , to maine un mein se eik aadmi ko talwaar di jab wo wapis aaya to usney kaha : kash ke aap ( wo halaat ( dekhtey jin par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein malamat ki . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum is baat se aajiz (majboor) they ke jab merey bhejey huey aadmi ne merey ehkam ki tanfeez (laagu) nahin ki to tum uski jagah kisi aur ko muqarrar kar letey jo merey ehkam ki tanfeez karta?''"
2628,Hazrat Abu Sa'alba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mujahideen jab kisi manzil par padaaw kartey they. ... . Amr bin Usman ke alfaz hain. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) padaaw kartey they. ... . to log wadiyon aur ghaatiyon mein bikhar jatey they. isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhara in wadiyon aur ghaatiyon mein bikhar jana shaitan ki taraf se hai.'' chunanche uskey baad jab bhi aap kisi manzil par padaaw kartey to Sahaba kiram eik doosrey ke bahut hi qarib rehtey yahan tak ke kaha jata : agar un par eik hi kapda taan diya jaey to sab par aa jaey.
2629,Hazrat Muaz bin Anas Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke falan falan ghazwey mein main Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ham-rikaab (sath) tha to logon ne manzilon par padaaw karney aur khemey waghaira laganey mein bahut tangi ka muzahira kiya ke raasta bhi na chhoda . to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna eik manadi bheja jisney logon mein aelan kiya : ''jo shakhs kheme laganey mein tangi karey ya raasta kaatey to uska jihad nahin.''
2630,"Sehal bin Muaz apney walid ( Hazrat Muaz bin Anas Juhni (Raziallahu anhu)) se bayan kartey hain, unhoney kaha : ham ne Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ghazwey mein shirkat ki . aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya."
2631,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) ne Salim Abun Nazar ko likha , jabkey wo harooriya logon ki taraf nikley they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney eik ghazwey mein , jab wo dushman se takraey they, farmaya tha : '' logo ! dushman se milney ki tamanna mat karo, Allah taala se aafiyat maango , magar jab us se mudbhed ho jaey to phir sabr aur sabaat (mazbooti) se kaam lo aur jaan lo ke jannat talwaaron ke saye taley hai.'' phir (ye) dua farmaee : ''aey Allah ! kitab ko nazil kerney waley ! baadalon ko chalaney waley ! lashkaron ko paspa kerney waley ! unhen paspa kar dey aur hamen un par nusrat aur ghalba ata farma.''"
2632,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ghazwey ke liye tashrif ley jatey to yun dua farmatey : (اللهم أنت عضدي و نصيري ، بك أحول وبك أصول وبك أقاتل) ''aey Allah ! to mera bazu aur mera madadgar hai, teri hi madad se main chalta phirta aur hamla karta hun aur ladaai karta hun.''"
2633,Ibne Aun (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke maine Janab Naafe ko likh bheja aur un se ye masla puchha ke qitaal (jang) ke moqe par mushrekin ko dawat dena kya hukm rakhta hai? to unhoney mujhey likh bheja : be-shak ye hukm ibtadaaey Islam mein tha. (iske baad) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qabeela bano mustaliq par hamla kiya jabkey wo ghafil they aur unke janwer pani pi rahey they to aapney unke ladney walon ko qatl kiya aur baaqiyon ko qaid kar liya . isi moqe par Juweriya binte Haris aap ke haath lagi thin .) baad mein Harame nabwi mein dakhil ki gaeen ( Naafe kehtey hain ke mujhey ye hadees Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan ki aur wo us lashkar mein shareek they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye hadees umda hai. isey ibne  Aun ne Naafe se bayan kiya hai. ibne  Aun ka is mein aur koi shareek nahin.
2634,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaze-Fajr ke waqt shabb khoon maara kartey they (be-khabri mein hamla karte then). aur (is se pehley ( kaan laga kar suntey, agar Azan ki aawaz sun letey to baaz rehtey warna hamla kar detey."
2635,Hazrat Isaam Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ham ko eik jihaadi muhim mein rawana kiya aur farmaya : ''jab tum koi masjid dekho ya kisi muazzan ko suno to phir kisi ko qatl na karna.''
2636,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya ''jang chaal ka naam hai.''"
2637,Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi taraf ghazwey ka irada farmatey to kisi aur janib ka ishara kartey. aur farmaya kartey : ''jang chaal ka naam hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke (الحرب خدعة) ka lafz is riwayat mein sirf Maamer hi ne is sanad se bayan kiya hai. jo dar-haqeeqat Amr bin Dinar An Jaabir ki sanad mein aaya hai) jo ooper zikr hui hai) aur isi tarah An Hammam ibne Munabbi An Abu Hurera ki sanad mein bhi waarid hai.
2638,"Janab Ayas bin Salma apney walid ( Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ko hamara ameer banaya , phir ham mushrekin se jihad ke liye nikley . ham ne un par raat mein be-khabri mein hamla kiya. us raat hamara shiaar tha ( أمت أمت ( Salma kehtey hain ke us raat maine apney haath se saat gharon ke mushrekin ko qatl kiya tha."
2639,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) daurane safar mein peechhey raha kartey they, zaeefon ki sawari haank ley jatey aur unhen apney peechhey bitha letey aur unke liye duayen kartey."
2640,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke mushrikon se qitaal karun yahan tak ke wo ( La-ilaah-illallah (ka iqrar kar lein , jab wo iska iqrar kar lein , to unhoney mujh se apney khoon aur maal mehfooz kar liye , siwaye iskey ke is iqrar (Islam) ka koi haq ho aur (dili maamlat mein) unka hisab Allah par hai.''"
2641,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey ye hukm diya gaya hai ke logon se qitaal karun yahan tak ke wo gawahi den ke Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud nahin aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain, aur wo hamarey qibley ki taraf rukh karen, hamara zabiha khaeyn aur hamari tarah Namaz padhein , log jab ye sab kuchh keren to unke khoon aur maal ham par haram hongey siwaey iske ke is (kalma tauheed aur Islam) ka koi haq ho. unke huqooq wohi hongey jo musalmanon ke hain aur unke faraaiz bhi wohi hongey jo musalmanon ke hain.''"
2642,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey mushrekin se qitaal ka hukm diya gaya hai.''  aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kiya."
2643,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ham logon ko eik muhim mein huruqaat (qabiley) ki taraf rawana farmaya , unhoney hamari khabar sun li aur nikal bhagey , ham ne eik aadmi ko ja liya jab ham ne usko gher liya to usney (La-ilaah-illallah) keh diya. ham ne usko maara yahan tak ke qatl kar diya. maine ye waqia Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney bayan kiya to aapney farmaya : ''qiyamat ke din ( La-ilaah-illallah (ke muqabley mein terey liye kon hoga?'' maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! usney ye hathiyar ke khof se kaha tha. aapney farmaya : ''bhala to ne uska dil kyon na cheer liya yahan tak ke tujhey maloom ho jata ke usney is wajeh se kaha tha ya kisi aur wajeh se? qiyamat ke din terey liye ( La-ilaah-illallah (ke muqabley mein kon hoga?'' aap ye kalma dohraatey rahey yahan tak ke mera dil chaha , kash ke main aaj hi Islam laya hota. ( mujh se ye gunahe azeem sarzad na hua hota.)"
2644,"Hazrat Miqdad bin Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main agar kisi kafir se takraaoon , wo mujh se qitaal karey aur talwaar se mera eik haath kaat daley , phir ( merey waar kerney par) kisi darkht ki ot le-ley aur kahe : maine Allah ke liye Islam qubul kiya. to aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya main usey qatl karun (ya na ( jabkey usney ( La-ilaah-illallah ( keh diya ho? aapney farmaya : ''usey qatl mat karo.'' maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! usney mera eik haath kaat dala hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey qatl mat karo, agar to ne usko qatl kar diya to wo terey maqam par hoga jahan ke to usko qatl kerney se pehley tha. (ma'soom khoon aur uska qatl haram tha.) aur to uski jagah par hoga jahan ke wo ye kalma kehney se pehley tha.'' (halal khoon aur uska qatl karna halal tha.)"
2645,"Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qabeela khash'am ki taraf eik muhim rawana farmaee to un mein se kuch logon ne sajda karkey panah hasil kerni chahi lekin) mujahideen ne unko ( jaldi jaldi qatl kar dala. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye khabar pahunchi to aapney unko aadhi diyat deney ka hukm diya. aur farmaya : ''main har us musalman se bari hun jo mushrekin ke andar muqeem ho.'' unhoney puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kyon? aapney farmaya : ''yani dono ko eik doosrey ki aag dikhai na dey (abadi is qadr door door honi chahiye). Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is hadees ko Hasheem, Maamer, Khalid Waasti aur kaee logon ne riwayat kiya hai aur unhoney Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) ka wastey zikr nahin kiya."
2646,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke jab ye aayat kareema nazil hui : (إن يكن منكم عشرون صابرون يغلبوا مائتين) ''agar tum mein bees huey sabr kerney waley to wo do-sau par ghalib aa jaeyngey.'' to musalmanon ko ye Amr (mamla) bada bhari mehsoos hua ke Allah ne farz kar diya hai ke eik aadmi das ke muqabley se na bhagey. phir (ye) kami nazil hui : ( الآن خفف الله عنكم . ... ( ''ab Allah ne tum se kami kar di hai aur usney jaan liya hai ke tum mein kamzori hai, so agar tum mein sau afrad huey sabir aur Sabit qadam to wo do-sau par ghalib hongey.'' Abu-Tooba Rabeea ( raawi hadees ( ne ye aayat kareema : ( يغلبوا مائتين ( tak padhi . kaha ke jab Allah taala ne ginti mein kami farma di to is aetbar se sabr mein bhi kami kar di."
2647,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki janib se bheji gaee eik muhim mein shareek they. to log ( mujahideen ( muqabley se bhag chaley aur main bhi un ( bhagney walon ( mein shareek tha. jab ham alehda huye, to ham ne kaha : kaisey karen, ham to jihad se bhag aaye hain aur) Allah ka ( ghazab lekar lautey hain? ham ne kaha : ham Madiney chaltey hain, wahan thehren gey aur (kisi dusri muhim mein) shareek ho jaeyngey aur hamein koi nahin dekhega , so jab ham Madiney aaye to ham ne socha kyon na apney aap ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke huzur pesh kar den , agar tauba qubul hui to ( behtar ( thehrey rahengey , warna jihad mein chaley jaeyngey . chunanche namaze-Fajr se pehley ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke intizar mein baith gaey . jab aap bahir nikley to ham aap ki taraf badhey aur kaha : ham log bhagodey hain. aap hamari taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : ''nahin, tum dobara ladaai mein janey waley ho.'' chunanche ham aap ke qarib huey aur aap ke haath ko bosa diya. aapney farmaya : ''main musalmanon ki jaey panah hun.''"
2648,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Badr ke din ye aayat nazil hui thi : (ومن يولهم يومئذ دبره - - - - - - - -) ''jisney is din, un (kuffar) se peeth pheri siwaye us haal ke ki paintraa badlta ho ladaai mein, ya kisi jamaat ki panah leta ho.'' (to wo mustashnaa hai, warna wo Allah ke ghazab ke sath lauta aur uska thikana dozakh hai aur ye bahut bura thikana hai). ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( : hamen khabar di Imam al-haafiz abu-Bakar Ahmed bin Ali bin Sabit khateeb Baghdaadi ne , kaha : Imam Qazi Abu-Amr Qasim bin Jaafar bin Abdul-Waahid Haashmi ne kaha : hamein khabar di Abu-Ali Muhammad bin Ahmed bin Amr Laulwee ne , unhoney kaha : hamein bayan kiya Abu-Dawud Sulaiman bin Ash'as Sajistaani (Rahimahullah) ne maahe mohrram sun do-sau pachhattar hijri mein . ... . farmaya."
2649,"Hazrat Khabbab bin Arat (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey jabke aap eik chadar ko takiya banaey Kaaba ke saye mein letey huey they. ham ne aap se shikayat ki aur kaha : kya aap hamarey liye madad nahin maangtey ? kya aap hamarey liye Allah se dua nahin farmatey ? to aap uth bethey, aap ka chehra surkh ho gaya aur farmaya : ''tum se pehley jo log they un mein se kisi ko pakda jata aur uskey liye gadha khoda jata, phir aara laya jata aur uskey sar par rakh kar usey do hissey kar diya jata magar ye ( azab bhi) usey uskey deen se na pherta tha, aur (wo kisi ke sath yun kartey ke) uski haddiyon tak gosht aur putthon mein lohey ki kanghiyan chalatey, ye karrwai bhi usey uskey deen se na pherti thi. Allah ki qasam ! Allah azz-w-jall apna ye deen pura karkey rahega yahan tak ke eik Sawar Sana aur hazare-maut ke darmiyan safar kerega, usey Allah ke siwa kisi ka khof na hoga ya ( ziyada se ziyada ( bakriyon ke mutalliq andesha hoga ke bhediya na hamla kar dey lekin tum jaldi kar rahey ho.'' (yani sabr w tahammul se kaam lo, Allah madad kerega.)"
2650,"Ubaidullah bin abi Raafe (Rahimahullah) Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ke kaatib ( secretery ( they, unhoney kaha : maine Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey , Zuber aur Miqdad ko rawana kya aur farmaya : '' jao yahan tak ke jab tum rauza khaakh ke maqam par pahuncho gey to tumhen eik oontni Sawar aurat milegi uskey paas eik khat hai, wo us se ley aao .'' chunanche ham rawana huey hamarey ghodey hamen badi tezi se liye ja rahey they yahan tak ke ham maqam rauza par pahunch gaey, to ham ne wahan eik aurat pai jo apni oontni par Sawar thi. ham ne us se kaha : lao khat dey do . usney kaha : merey paas koi khat nahin hai. maine kaha : ya to to khat nikalegi ya ham terey kapdey utaar dengey . chunanche usney apni chutiya mein se khat nikal diya, to usey lekar ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aagey . wo Haatib bin abi Balta' ki taraf se mushrekin ko likha gaya tha, us mein unko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baaz maamlat ke mutalliq khabar di gaee thi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha '' Haatib ! ye kya hai? '' usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujh par jaldi ( mein faisla ( na kijiye , darasal mein ehle-Quraish mein naya abad tha, khas qabeela Quraish se mera talluq nahin tha jabkey ( muhajrin ( Quraish ke wahan Makka mein dusrey talluqdaar mojud hain jo unke ghar-parivar ki hifazat kartey hain lihaza maine chaha ke mujhey unke sath talluq daari ka koi wasta hasil nahin hai, to main un par eik ehsan kar dun jiski bina par wo merey qurbat daaron ka khayal rakhen . Allah ki qasam ! aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujh mein koi kufr nahin hai aur na main deen se phira hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sach kaha hai. '' Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mujhey chodiye mein us munafiq ki gardan uda dun . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye badr mein shareek ho chuka hai aur tumhen kya khabar, shayad Allah taala ne ehle-badr par nazar farmaai ho aur kaha hai ke jo chahey karo, tehqiq maine tumhen bakhsh diya hai. ''"
2651,"Hazrat abu-Abdur-Rehman Sulami Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se ye qissa bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Haatib (Raziallahu anhu) ne ehle-Makka ko likha tha ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumhari taraf rukh kerney waley hain. us riwayat mein hai ke us aurat ne kaha : merey paas khat nahin hai. to ham ne uski oontni ko bitha liya magar hamen uskey paas koi khat na mila Hazrat Ali boley : qasm us zaat ki jiski qasam uthai jati hai! main tujhey qatl kar dalunga, nahin to khat nikal dey. aur hadees bayan ki."
2652,"Hazrat Faraat bin Hayyan (Raziallahu anhu)) apney mutalliq ( bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko qatl kerney ka hukm diya tha jabkey wo abu-Sufiyaan ki taraf se jaasoos bin kar aaya tha. ye eik Ansari ka haleef bhi tha. wo Ansariyon ki eik jamaat ke paas se guzra aur kaha : be-shak main musalman hun. to eik Ansari ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! ye kehta hai ke main musalman hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein kuch log aisey hain ke ham unko unke emaan ke sipurd kar detey hain, un mein se Faraat bin Hayyan bhi hai. ''"
2653,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik safar mein mushrekin ka koi jaasoos Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur Sahaba ke sath betha raha , phir khamoshi se khisak gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey dhoondo aur qatl kar dalo.'' Hazrat Salma ne kaha : maine doosron se pehley usko ja liya aur qatl kar diya aur uska saman ley aaya. pas aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wo saman mujhey hi bator nafl ( inaam ( inayat farma diya."
2654,"Hazrat Ayas bin Salma kehtey hain, mujh se merey walid (Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bayan kya, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath qabila Hawazin par jihad kya. ittifaq se ham chaasht ke waqt khana kha rahey they aur ham mein aksar mujahideen pedal they aur kuch log kamzor bhi they, itney main eik shakhs aaya jo surkh oont par Sawar tha, usney oont ki kamar se rassi nikali, us se usko baandha aur aa kar logon ke sath khaney mein shareek ho gaya. jab usney dekha ke mujahideen mein kamzor log hain aur un mein sawariyon ki bhi kami hai to wahan se nikla , bhaagta hua apney oont ke paas pahuncha aur usey khola , usko bithaya , khud us par betha aur phir usey daudaatey huey chal diya. (us waqt ham ko yaqeen ho gaya ke ye jasus hai) chunanche qabeela Aslam ka eik shakhs apni khakastri oontni par uska pichha kartey huey gaya, aur ye oontni hamari sab sawaariyon se umda sawari thi. Salma kehtey hain : main pedal hi bhaagta hua uskey peechey gaya aur usey ja liya jabkey oontni ka sar oont ki raan ke paas tha aur main oontni ki pichli taangon ke sath tha. phir main aagey badha yahan tak ke oont ki pichli taangon ke paas pahunch gaya. mein aur aagey badha yahan tak ke oont ki nakel pakad li aur phir usko bitha liya . jab usney apna ghutna zameen par rakha to maine apni talwaar nikali aur us Sawar ke sar par dey maari to wo kat kar door ja gira , chunanche main uska oont aur jo us par tha sab haank kar ley aaya . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne logon se aagey badh kar mera istaqbal kya aur puchha : '' us aadmi ko kis ne qatl kya hai? '' Sahaba ne kaha : Salma bin Akwa ne , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uska sara asbab usi ka hai. '' ( Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ke Shekh ( Harun ne kaha : us riwayat ke alfaz haashim bin Qasim ke hain."
2655,"Hazrat Noman bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan hazir raha hun, aap agar din ke ibtidaai (shuruati) hissey mein qitaal na kartey to us mein itni takheer farmatey ke Suraj dhal jata , hawaeyn chalney lagtin aur nusrat nazil hoti."
2656,Hazrat Qais bin Ibaad (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba qitaal ke doran mein aawazen nikalney ko napasand kartey they.
2657,Hazrat abu-Barda apney walid (Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu)) se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi ki misl riwayat kartey hain.
2658,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hunain ke din jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka mushrekin ke sath muqabla hua aur musalman aap ke paas se bhag gaey, to aap apney khachar se nichey utar kar pedal ho gaey."
2659,"Hazrat Jabir bin Ateek (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : '' ghairat ke kuch andaz Allah taala ko mehboob aur kuch napasand hain, Allah azz-w-jall ki pasandida ghairat wo hai jo shubhe ki bina par ho, magar aisi ghairat jo baghair kisi shubha ke ho, Allah taala ko napasand hai. usi tarah badai ka izhar bhi kuch aisa hai jo Allah ko napasand hai aur kuch pasandida hai. pasandida badai ka izhar wo hai jo qitaal ke waqt Mujahid apney mutalliq karta hai ya sadqa kartey waqt ho, aur badai ka izhar jo Allah taala ko napasand hai wo hai jo zulm aur تعدی mein ho.'' Musa bin Ismael ( Shekh Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ( ne ( naa-pasandida badai ke izhar mein) '' nasab mein fakhr '' ka bhi zikr kya."
2660,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi karim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne das afrad ko bator jasus rawana kya aur un par Hazrat Aasim bin Sabit ko ameer muqarrar kya, to qabeela huzail ke taqriban eik so teer andaz unke muqabley mein aa gaey. jab Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko dekha to ye sab eik tiley ki ot mein ho gaey ( magar un kafiron ne unko gher liya (aur boley : hathiyar phenk do aur apney aap ko hamarey hawaley kar do , ham tum se ye ehad kartey hain aur pukhta wada hai ke tum mein se kisi ko qatl na karengey . Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main kisi kafir ke ehad mein nahin aata . to unhoney un mujahideen ko teer maarey aur Aasim samet saat afrad ko qatl kar diya, aur teen afrad ne un kafiron ka ehad w meesaaq qubul kar liya . ye they khubaib aur Zaid bin Wasna aur eik aur aadmi (us ka naam Abdullah bin Tariq Balwi aaya hai.) jab un kafiron ne unko pakad liya to unhoney unki kamanon ki taantein kholin aur un se unko baandh diya. teesra aadmi kehney laga : ye pehla dhoka hai, Allah ki qasam ! main tumharey sath nahin chalunga. merey liye merey ( qatl ho janey waley ( sathi hi namoona hain. unhoney usko ghasita magar usney unke sath chalney se inkar kar diya to unhoney usko qatl kar diya. (aur khubaib aur Zaid ko unhoney Makka ley ja kar bech diya. Hazrat khubaib ko Haris bin Aamir ke beton ne kharid liya) chunanche khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) (unke) qaidi ho gaey yahan tak ke unhoney unko qatl kerney ka faisla kar liya. (mutaiyena taareekh se pehley) khubaib ne un se ustara talab kya taake zer-naaf baal saaf kar saken, jab wo unko qatl kerney ke liye ley chaley , to khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mujhey mohlat do main do rakaat ada kar lun . phir kaha : qasam Allah ki ! agar mujhey ye shubha na hota ke tum log samjhogey ke dar ke maarey Namaz padhta hai to main aur ziyada padhta."
2661,ibn Auf ki sanad hai ke Zohri ne kaha : mujhey Amr bin abi Sufiyan bin Usaid bin Jariya Saqafi ne bayan kya aur ye bani zohra ke haleef aur Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ke shagirdon mein se they aur hadees bayan ki .
2662,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ahad waley din teer andazon ke jathay par Hazrat Abdullah bin Jubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko ameer muqarrar kya, un logon ki tadaad pachas thi aur un se farmaya tha : ''agar tum dekho ke parindey hamen uchak rahey hain, tab bhi tum ye jagah na chhodna yahan tak ke main tumhen koi pegham bhejun . aur agar tum dekho ke ham ne kafiron ko shikast de-di hai aur ham unko raund rahey hain, tab bhi tum yahin rehna yahan tak ke main tumhen bulwaaun .'' bayan kartey hain ke Allah taala ne kafiron ko shikast se dochaar kar diya. qasam Allah ki ! maine dekha unki aurten ( panah ke liye ( pahad par chadh rahi thin . to Abdullah bin Jubair ke) teer andaz ( sathiyon ne kaha : ghanimat ! aey qom ghanimat ! tumharey sathi ghalib aagey hain, tum kya dekh rahey ho? Abdullah bin Jubair ne kaha : kya tum bhool gaey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne tum se kya farmaya tha. unhoney kaha : qasam Allah ki ! ham to logon ke sath mil kar ghanimat jama karengey . chunanche wo chaley aaye , to unke munh pher diye gaey aur shikast se dochaar huey ."
2663,"Hazrat Hamza bin abi Usaid apney walid ( abu-Usaid Malik bin Rabeea Ansari (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain unhoney kaha : jab ham ne Badr mein safein bana lin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab wo tumharey qarib hon (tumhari zad mein aa jaeyn) to teer maarna aur apney teeron ko mehfooz rakhna.'' (bila zarurat teer na chalaana, taake teer mehfooz rahen.)"
2664,Hazrat Malik bin Hamza bin abi Usaid Saaidi apney walid se wo dada (abu-Usaid Malik bin Rabeea Ansari (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne badr waley din farmaya : ''jab wo tumharey qarib aa jaeyn (aur tumhari zad mein hon) tab un par teer maarna aur talwaar bhi usi waqt soontna jab wo tum par chha jaeyn.'' (aur talwaar ki maar par hon.)
2665,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke (jange-badr mein) Utba bin Rabeea samney aaya aur uskey peechey uska beta aur bhai bhi aagey to usney lalkaara: kon hai jo muqabley mein aaye? us par Ansari jawan samney aaye. usney puchha : tum kon ho? to unhoney usko bata diya (ke ham Ansari jawan hain) usney kaha : hamen tum se koi matlab nahin. ham apney chacha zaad chahtey hain. to Nabi karim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : utho, aey Hamza! ''utho, aey Ali! utho, aey Ubeda bin Haris! '' chunanche Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) Utba ke muqabil huey aur main ( Ali ( Sheba ke samney aaya . Ubeda aur Waleed ke darmiyan do do waron ka muqabla hua aur her eik ko eik doosrey se chotein lagin (aur zakhmi huey) phir ham dono Waleed par chadh dodey aur usko qatl kar dala aur Ubeda ko utha laye ."
2666,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qatl kerney ke maamley mein sab se achey log ahle-eman hotey hain. '' ( wo maqtool ke naak kaan waghera nahin kaat'tey .)"
2667,"Hazrat Hayyaj bin Imran se marwi (bayan) hai, ( kehtey hain ( ke) merey walid ( imran ka eik ghulam bhag gaya to usney Allah ki qasam khai ke agar wo merey haath aa gaya to uska haath kaat dalunga. pas usney mujhey (Hayyaj ko) bheja ke ye masla poochhun . to main Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur un se daryaft kya, to unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen sadqa deney ki targheeb diya kartey they aur) maqtool ka ( musla kerney se mana farmaya kartey they. mein phir Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke paas aaya aur un se bhi daryaft kya, to unhoney bhi yehi kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen sadqa deney ki targheeb diya kartey they aur maqtool ka musla kerney se mana farmaya kartey they."
2668,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke kisi ghazwey mein dekha gaya ke eik aurat ko qatl kya gaya hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aurton aur bachon ke qatl ko bahut bura jana ."
2669,"Hazrat Ribah bin Rabeea bayan kartey hain ke ham eik ghazwey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they, aapney dekha ke log kisi chiz par ikhattey ho rahey hain. aapney eik aadmi ko bheja ke dekh kar aaye wo kyon jama hain? wo ho kar aaya aur bataya : eik aurat qatl ki gaee hai aur wo us par jama hain. pas aapney farmaya : ''ye to ladney wali na thi .'' bayan kya ke us fauj ke muqadme par Khalid bin Waleed they. aapney eik shakhs ko bheja ke Khalid se keh do : '' kisi aurat ya kisi mazdoor ko hergiz qatl na keren .''"
2670,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mushrekin ke boodhon ko qatl karo aur nojawanon (nabaligh bachon ( ko zinda rehney do .''"
2671,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke) yahudiyon ke qabiley) bani Qureza ki aurton mein se sirf eik aurat ko qatl kya gaya tha, wo merey paas bethi baaten kar rahi thi aur itna hansti thi ke uskey pet aur kamar mein bal pad jatey they halanke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baazar mein uski qom ke logon ko qatl kiye ja rahey they. achcha eik pukarney waley ne us aurat ka naam pukara ke fulani kahan hai? wo kehney lagi : main hun. maine puchha : tera kya qissa hai? kehney lagi : maine eik saazishi kaam kya hai. chunanche wo pukarney wala usey ley gaya aur phir uski gardan maar di gaee . Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain : main usey nahin bholi hun aur us par tajjub hota hai ke usey maloom tha ke wo qatl honey wali hai magar wo hans hans kar lot pot ho rahi thi."
2672,"Hazrat Saab bin Jassama (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya tha ke mushrekin ke ghar walon ka kya hukm hai jabkey un par hamla kiya jata hai to chhotey bachey aur aurten bhi uski zad mein aa jatey hain, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo bhi unhi mein se hain.'' aur Amr (bin Dinar ( kaha kartey they : '' wo bhi apney aaba mein se hain.'' Zohri (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey baad aurton aur bachon ke qatl se mana farma diya tha."
2673,"Muhammad bin Hamza Aslami apney walid ( Hamza bin umr Aslami ( se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko eik dastey ka ameer banaya tha. kehtey hain ke jab main rawana hua to aapney farmaya : ''agar tumhen falan shakhs mil jaey to usko aag se jala dena .'' maine peeth pheri to aapney mujhey bulaya main aap ke paas wapis aaya, to aapney farmaya : ''agar tum falan ko pao to usey qatl kar dena, jalaana nahin, bila-shuba aag se azab aag ka rab hi dey sakta hai. ''"
2674,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ham ko eik muhim par rawana kya aur farmaya : ''agar tum falan falan ko pao . . . . .'' aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya.
2675,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abdullah apney walid ( Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke eik safar mein ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they. aap qazaey-hajat ke liye gaey to ham ne eik chidiya dekhi, uskey sath do bachey bhi they, ham ne uskey dono bachey pakad liye to chidiya aai aur) bachon ke ooper ird-gird ( mandlaane lagi . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur farmaya : '' kis ne usko uskey bachon se pareshan kya hai? uskey bachon ko chhod do .'' ( eik doosrey moqe par) aapney dekha ke chewntiyon ke badey bil ko ham ne jala dala hai? aapney puchha : '' usko kis ne jalaaya hai? '' ham ne kaha : ham ne jalaaya hai. aapney farmaya : '' aag ke rab ke siwa kisi ko munasib nahin ke aag se azab dey .''"
2676,"Hazrat Waasila bin Isqaa (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke ghazwa tabuk ke moqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aelan jihad farmaya to main apney ghar walon ke paas gaya , wapis aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ka pehla qafla rawana ho chuka tha. mein Madiney mein ghoomney laga aur aelan karta tha : koi hai jo eik aadmi ko apney sath Sawar kara ley aur uski ghanimat ka hissa paey ? to eik Ansari boodhey ne kaha : uski ghanimat ka hissa hamara hoga aur ham usey baari se apney sath Sawar karaengey aur wo khana bhi hamarey sath khaeyga? maine kaha : bahut behtar. usney kaha : to chaliye Allah taala ki barkat ke sath . chunanche main eik behtareen sathi ke sath rawana hua. yahan tak ke Allah ne hamen maale-ghanimat diya aur mujhey kuch oontniyaan milin , main unhen apney sathi ke paas haank laya , chunanche wo apney oont ke kajawey par pichley hissey par betha aur mujhey kaha : unhen chalaao ke main unhen peechey ki taraf se dekhun . phir kaha : unhen chalaao ke main unhen aagey ki taraf se dekhun . wo bola : tumhari oontniyan bahut umda hain. maine arz kya ye to aap ki ghanimat hain jiski mein aap se shart kar chuka hun. usney kaha : bhatijey ! apni oontniyan ley jao, ham ne terey doosrey hissey ka irada kya hai. (ajr w sawab mein hissey daari ka.)"
2677,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' hamarey rab azz-w-jall ko aisey logon par tajjub aata hai jo zanjeeron mein jakdey jannat ki taraf ley jaey jaeyngey .''
2678,"Hazrat Jundub bin Makees (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abdullah bin ghalib Lesi (Raziallahu anhu) ko eik dasta de-kar rawana kya, main un logon mein shamil tha, aapney hukm diya ke maqam kudaid mein bani Mulawweh par (her taraf sey) chadhai karna , chunanche ham rawana huey yahan tak ke maqam kudaid par pahunch gaey . ham ko Haris bin Barsa Lesi mila, ham ne usko pakad liya . usney kaha : main Islam qubul karna chahta hun aur main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan janey ki niyat hi se nikla hun. ham ne us se kaha : agar to haqiqat mein musalman hai, to hamara tujhey eik din aur raat ke liye baandh lena terey liye koi nuqsan deh nahin hai. aur agar to aisey na hua to (tujhey baandh kar) ham teri taraf se be fikr ho jaeyngey. chunanche ham ne usko rassi se jakad liya."
2679,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Najad ki taraf eik jihaadi dasta rawana farmaya. wo qabeela banu-Hanifa ka eik aadmi pakad laye jiska naam Samama bin Assal tha aur wo ehle Yamama ka sardar tha. chunanche unhoney usey masjid ke eik sutoon ke sath baandh diya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey paas aaye aur puchha : Samama! terey paas kya hai? (ya tera kya khayal hai?) usney kaha : aey Muhammad! merey paas khair hai. agar tum ne qatl kya to eik khoon waley ko qatl karogey . aur agar ehsan karogey to eik shukr guzar par ehsan karogey . agar aap ko maal ki zarurat ho to kahey jitna chahtey ho milega . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey usi haal par rehney diya. agla din hua to aapney us se phir puchha : Samama ! terey paas kya hai? (ya tera kya khayal hai? ( to usney pehley jaisi baat dohrani. pas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey usi haal par rehney diya. yahan tak ke aglaa din hua to bhi yehi mukalma hua. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Samama ko azad kar do.'' chunanche wo chala gaya aur masjid ke qarib nakhlistan mein pahuncha, wahan ja kar ghusl kya aur phir masjid mein wapis aa gaya aur kehney laga : (أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله وأشهد أن محمدا عبده ورسوله) ''main gawahi deta hun ke eik Allah ke siwa koi mabud nahin aur gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain.'' aur dono ne puri hadees bayan ki. Esa bin Hammad ne kaha : ham ko Leis bin Saad ne khabar di to usmein (إن تقتل تقتل ذا دم) ki bajaey (ذا ذم) ke lafz bayan kiye. (agar qatl kya to) eik sahab zimma aur ehtiraam waley ko qatl karogey, (mafhoom dono ka ye hai ke meri qom badla legi.)"
2680,"Hazrat Yahya bin Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman bin Saad bin Zarara se riwayat hai ke Badr ke qaidiyon ko jab laya gaya to ummul-momenin Sauda bint Zam-aa (Raziallahu anha) aale-Ifra ke paas yani Ifra ke sahibzadon Auf aur Muawwiz ke yahan thehri hui thin, jahan ke unke oonton ka baada tha. aur ye ummahatul-momenin par parda farz honey se pehley ka waqia hai. Sauda (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain : Allah ki qasam ! main un logon (aale-Ifra) ke yahan thi jab main (wahan sey) aai to mujhey bataya gaya ke qaidi laye gaey hain. main apney ghar lauti, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wahan tashrif farma they aur abu-Zaid Suhel bin Amr bhi hujrey ke koney mein pada tha. eik rassi se uskey haathon ko uski gardan ke sath baandh diya gaya tha. ... . phir baqi hadees bayan ki . Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke un dono ne ( Auf aur Muawwiz ne ( abu-Jahal bin Hisham ko qatl kya tha. ye uski taraf badhey they magar pehchantey na they aur khud Badr ke roz Shahid ho gaey they."
2681,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney as-haab ko bulaya aur phir Badr ki taraf rawana huey . to achcha unhen Quraish ke oont miley jin par wo pani dhotey they, un mein bani Hajjaj ka kalay rang ka eik ghulam bhi tha, Sahaba ne usko pakad liya aur us se chhaanbeen kerney lagey ke abu-Sufiyaan kahan hai? usney kaha : Allah ki qasam ! mujhey uskey maamley ki koi khabar nahin, lekin ye ehle-Quraish aaye hain, un mein abu-Jahal , Rabeea ke dono bete Utba w Sheba aur Umayya bin khalaf bhi hain. jab wo Sahaba ko ye baat kehta, to wo usey maarney lagtey. pas wo kehta : mujhey chhodo, mujhey chhodo, batata hun. jab usey chhod detey, tu kehta : Allah ki qasam! mujhey abu-Sufiyaan ka koi ilm nahin, lekin ye ehle-Quraish aaye hain, un mein abu-Jahal , Rabeea ke dono bete Utba w Sheba aur Umayya bin khalaf bhi hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padh rahey they aur ye sab sun rahey they. jab aap Namaz se farigh huey to farmaya : ''qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai! jab wo tumhen sach kehta hai, to tum maarney lagtey ho aur jab jhoot bolta hai, to usey chhod detey ho, ye Quraish ke log abu-Sufiyaan hi ko bachaney ke liye aaye hain.'' Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kal ye jagah falan ka maqtal hogi.'' aur aapney apna haath zameen par rakha.'' kal ye jagah falan ka maqtal hogi.'' aur aapney apna haath zameen par rakha.'' kal ye jagah falan ka maqtal hogi.'' aur aapney apna haath zameen par rakha . Anas kehtey hain : qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! un naamzad logon mein se koi eik bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke haath ki jagah se idhar-udhar na hua. so Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un maqtulon ke mutalliq hukm diya to unhen taangon se pakad pakad aur ghasit-ghasit kar Badr ke kunwen mein dal diya gaya."
2682,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney kaha : jab koi aurat aisi hoti ke uskey bachey zinda na rehtey, to wo nazar maan liya karti thi ke agar uska bacha zinda raha to wo usey yahudi bana dalegi. so jab bano Nazir ko Madiney se jala watan kya gaya to un mein Ansariyon ke ladkey bhi they. (jo us qism ki nazar ke tehat yahudi banaey gaey they) unhoney kaha : ham apney bachon ko nahin chodengey (unke sath nahin janey dengey) tu Allah taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaai : (لا إكراه في الدين قد تبين الرشد من الغي) '' deen mein koi jabr w ikrah nahin. hidayat , gumrahi ke muqabley mein wazeh aur numaya ho chuki hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ( المقلاة ( wo aurat hoti hai jiskey bachey zinda na rehtey hon."
2683,"Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Fateh Makka ke moqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chaar mardon aur do aurton ke siwa tamam logon ko aman de-di thi. raawi ne unke naam ginwaaey. aur ibne-abi-Sarah bhi they. aur hadees bayan ki . ibne-abi sarah Hazrat Usman bin Affan ke yahan chup gaey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab logon ko baiat ke liye bulaya , to Usman (Raziallahu anhu) un ( ibne-abi sarah ( ko ley aaye aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas khada kar diya aur arz kya : aey Allah ke Nabi ! Abdullah ki baiat qubul farma lijiye . aapney apna sar uthaya , unki taraf dekha, teen baar is tarah hua, aapney her baar uska inkar farmaya. teesri baar ke baad aapney un se baiat farma li. phir apney Sahaba ki taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : ''tum mein koi samajhdar aadmi na tha, jo uski taraf uthta, jab dekha ke maine uski baiat se haath khinch liya hai to usko qatl kar deta?'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! hamen maloom na tha ke aap ke ji mein kya hai? aap apni aankh se hamen ishara farma detey. aapney farmaya : ''nabi ko laaiq nahin ke uski aankh khaain ho.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Abdullah (bin abi Sarah) Hazrat Usman ke dudh sharik bhai they. aur Waleed bin Aqba Hazrat Usman ki maa ki taraf se bhai they. unhoney jab sharab pi thi to Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko had lagai thi."
2684,"Amr bin Usman bin Abdur-Rehman apney dada sey, wo apney walid se (Saeed bin Yarboo makhzumi (Raziallahu anhu) sey) riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka ke din farmaya tha : ''chaar logon ko main halal ya Haram mein (hudude-Haram mein ya us se bahir kahin bhi) panah nahin deta.'' chunanche unke naam ginwaaey. aur do londiyan thin jo gaaney bajaney ka kaam karti thin aur maqees ki milkiyat thin eik ko qatl kar diya gaya aur dusri bhag nikli aur baad mein Islam ley aai . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : main is hadees ki sanad ( apney Shekh ( Muhammad bin Ala se kamaa-haqqahu nahin samajh saka tha."
2685,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Fateh Makka ke moqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka mein dakhil huye, to aap ke sar par khud thi. jab aapney usey utaara to aap ke paas eik aadmi aaya aur bataya ke ibne-khatal Kaaba ke pardon ke sath chimta hua hai. aapney farmaya : ''usko qatl kar dalo. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ibn khatal ka naam Abdullah tha aur Hazrat abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko qatl kya tha."
2686,Janab Ibrahim Nakhai (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Suhaak bin Qais ne irada kya ke Masruq ko aamil banaey. to Umara bin Aqba ne kaha : kya tum aisey aadmi ko aamil banana chahtey ho jo Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke qaatilon mein se baqi reh gaya hai? to Masruq ne us se kaha : hamen Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya aur wo hamarey nazdik hadees bayan kerney mein moatabar they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab terey baap (Aqba bin abi mueet) ko qatl kerney ka irada kya to us (Aqba) ne kaha : merey bachon ka kafeel kon hoga? aapney farmaya : '' aag '' so mein bhi terey liye wohi chiz pasand karta hun jisey terey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne pasand kya tha.
2687,(Ubaid) ibne-Ti-la ki riwayat hai ke ham ne Abdur-Rehman bin Khalid bin Waleed ke sath mein jihad kya. unke samney dushman kafir ke chaar afrad laye gaey jo ajmi they aur badey taqatwar they. pas unhoney Hakam diya aur unhen bandhey bandhey qatl kar diya gaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is hadees mein ibne-Wahab ke shagrid Saeed ke ilawa doosron ne hamen yun bayan kya ke '' unko teer se maara gaya jabkey wo bandhey huey they. '' Hazrat Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye khabar pahunchi to unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna hai : aap is tarah qatl kerney se mana farmatey they. (Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha) qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai! agar eik murghi bhi ho to usko baandh kar na maarun. Janab Abdur-Rehman bin Khalid ko ye khabar pahunchi to unhoney chaar gardanen azad kin.
2688,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke (safar Hudebiya mein) ehle-Makka ke assi ( 80 ( aadmi Fajr ki Namaz ke waqt tan-eem ke pahadon se utrey ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke as-haab ko qatl kar dalen magar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko pakad liya aur unhoney bhi apney aap ko unke hawaley kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baad mein unko riha kar diya tu Allah taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaai : (وهو الذي كف أيديهم عنكم وأيديكم عنهم ببطن مكة . . ۔) ''( Allah ( wo zaat hai jisney wadi Makka mein unke haathon ko tum se rokey rakha aur tumharey hathon ko un se rokey rakha.''
2689,Muhammad bin Jubair bin Mut-im apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Badr ke qaidiyon ke mutalliq farmaya : ''agar Mut-im bin Adi zinda hota aur mujh se un najas badbu-daron ke mutalliq baat karta to main uski khatir unko riha kar deta.''
2690,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jab Badr ka din tha aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qaidiyon se fidya liya to Allah taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaai : (ما كَانَ لِنَبِيٍّ أَنْ يَكُونَ لَهُ أَسْرَى حَتَّى يُثْخِنَ في الْأَرْضِ) ''nabi ko munasib nahin ke uskey liye qaidi hon yahan tak ke (dushman ko) zameen mein achi tarah kuchal ley, tum duniya ka maal chahtey ho aur Allah aakhirat chahta hai, aur Allah ghalib hai hikmat wala hai. agar Allah ka faisla pehley se likha hua na hota to jo kuch tum ne (fidya) liya hai us par tumhen bada azab pahunchta.'' phir Allah azz-w-jall ne unke liye ghanimaton ko halal farma diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : maine Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahimahullah) se suna ke un se Abu-Nooh ka naam puchha gaya to unhoney kaha : tum uskey naam ka kya karogey? uska naam qabih sa hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke uska naam ''قراد'' hai (cheechdi) aur sahih ye hai ke uska naam Abdur-Rehman bin ghazawan hai."
2691,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Badr ke moqe par ehle-jahiliyat ( mushrik qaidiyon) ka fidya char so (dirham fi kis) muqarrar kya tha.
2692,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke jab ehle-Makka ne apney qaidiyon ke fidye bhejey to Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sahibzadi ( ne ( apney shohar ( abul-Aas ke fidya mein maal bheja , aur wo haar pesh kya jo ummul-momenin Hazrat Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ne unko abul-Aas se shaadi ke waqt diya tha. usey dekh kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par shadeed rona aaya aur farmaya : ''agar tum munasib samjho to uskey qaidi ko uskey liye wesey hi riha kar do aur uska haar usey wapis kar do.'' Sahaba ne usey b-khushi qubul kya. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne abul-Aas se ye ehad liya ke Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ko aap ki taraf bhej dega. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Zaid bin Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) aur eik Ansari ko bheja aur unhen kaha : ''tum wadi yaajuj ke daman mein rukna yahan tak ke Zenab tumharey paas aa jaey to phir usey sath lekar aa jana.''"
2693,"Hazrat Marwan bin Hakam aur Miswar bin Makhrima ka bayan hai ke Hawazin ke musalman logon ka wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya to unhoney darkhast ki ke hamara maal wapis kar diya jaey ( jo ke ghazwae-Hunain mein musalmanon ke qabze mein aaya hai) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey sath ye log hain jin ko tum dekh rahey ho (mujahideen) aur mujhey baat wo pasand hai jo sachi ho, tum log do mein se eik chiz ikhtiyar kar lo, qaidi ya maal.'' unhoney kaha : ham apney qaidiyon ko ikhtiyar kartey hain, (unhen riha kar diya jaey) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutbe ke liye khadey huye, Allah azz-w-jall ki hamd w sana bayan ki phir farmaya : ''tumharey ye bhai tauba karkey aaye hain, maine ye munasib samjha hai ke unke qaidi unko wapis kar dun, to tum mein se bhi jo khushi khushi ye kaam karna chahey karey, aur jo pasand karey ke (uskey qaidi ke badley) usey uska hissey diya jaey to ye hamarey zimmey raha aur pehli pehli ghanimat jo Allah hamen dega us mein se ham uska haq ada karengey.'' logon ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham unke liye b-khushi ye kaam kartey hain. aapney farmaya : ''ham par ye wazeh nahin hai ke tum mein se kis ne ijazat di hai aur kis ne nahin di, lihaza tum jao yahan tak ke tumharey numaaindey hamen aa kar tumhara maamla bataeyn .'' chunanche wo log lot gaey, unke ameeron aur numaaindon ne un se ( khul kar) baat ki, to un numaaindon ne aa kar bataya ke hamarey log khushi se unhen ( azad kerney ki) ijazat dey rahey hain."
2694,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo (shoaib) apney dada se is waqiey ke silsiley mein bayan kartey hain ke phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' un logon ki aurten aur bachey unhen lota do aur jo koi bina kisi badley ke wapis na karna chahey to hamara us se wada hai ke pehli pehli ghanimat jo Allah taala hamen inayat farmaeyga us mein se chhe oont usey diye jaeyngey .'' phir aap apney oont ke qarib huey aur uskey kohan se kuch baal liye aur farmaya : '' logo ! is ghanimat mein se merey liye khums (paanchwen hissey) ke siwa kuch nahin hai, is qadr (baal) bhi nahin.'' aur aapney ishara kartey huey apni ungli buland farmaai. aur farmaya : ''ye khums bhi tum logon hi mein taqseem hoga, lihaza sui aur dhaagey tak wapis kar do.'' chunanche eik aadmi khada hua, uskey haath mein baalon ka eik guchcha sa tha wo bola : maine ye baal liye hain taake paalaan ke nichey ki guddi durust kar lun . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo mera zati hissa hai ya bani abdul-Muttalib ka , wo tum ley saktey ho ( doosron ka nahin .'' ( usney kaha : agar uska itna gunah hai jo main dekh raha hun to mujhey uski koi zarurat nahin aur usney guchcha phenk diya."
2695,Hazrat abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi qom par ghalib aa jatey to ( uskey baad) teen din tak unke ilaqey mein iqaamat farmatey . ibn Musanna ne kaha : jab aap kisi qom par ghalib aa jatey to pasand farmatey ke unke ilaqey mein teen din thehrein. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : muhaddis Yahya bin Saeed is hadees par aetraz kya kartey they ke ye Saeed (ibne-abi Aruba) ki purani riwayaat mein se nahin hai kyonkey 45 hijrii mein unka hafiza bigad gaya tha. aur unhoney ye hadees is bimari ke baad hi bayan ki hai. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : ( kaha jata hai ke Wakee ne un se ye hadees hafizey ki kharabi ke dino mein li thi. (
2696,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney eik londi aur uskey bachey mein judai kar di (aur unhen alehda alehda bech diya ( to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko us se rok diya aur unka ye sauda wapis kara diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Memun (bin abi shabeeb) ne Hazrat Ali ko nahin paya . ye 83 hijrii mein Jamajim mein qatl kar diye gaey they. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : waqia Harra 63 hijri mein hua tha aur Hazrat ( Abdullah ( ibne-Zubair 73 hijrii mein qatl huey they.
2697,"Hazrat Ayas bin Salma apney walid ( Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain, kehtey hain : ham Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath ( jihad ke liye ( rawana huey . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko hamara ameer banaya tha, ham ne bano Fazara ke sath jihad kya aur her taraf se un par chadhai ki . maine logon ki eik jamaat dekhi, un mein bachey they aur aurten bhi . maine eik teer maara jo unke aur pahad ke darmiyan ja gira to wo uth khadey huye, main unhen Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas ley aaya . un mein Fazara ki eik aurat thi jisney eik purani khaal odhi hui thi uskey sath uski beti bhi thi jo Arab ki Husain tareen ladkiyon mein se thi. abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne wo ladki bator ghanimat mujhey dey di. main Madiney aaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujhey miley aur farmaya : ''aey Salma ! wo aurat mujhey hiba kar dey .'' maine arz kya : qasam Allah ki ! wo to mujhey bahut pasand aai hai aur maine uska kapda bhi nahin uthaya . pas aap khamosh ho rahey . jab agla din hua, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujhey baazar mein miley aur farmaya : ''aey Salma! aurat mujhey hiba kar dey, terey baap ki bhalai ho.'' maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool! maine uska kapda tak nahin uthaya, magar wo aap ki hui. chunanche aapney usey ehle-Makka ki taraf bhej diya jabkey kuch musalman qaidi unke qabzey mein they, to us aurat ko bator fidye ke unko dey diya."
2698,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke unka eik ghulam bhag kar dushmanon ke paas chala gaya. phir musalman un logon par ghalib aagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wo ghulam ibne-Umar ko wapis kar diya aur (bator ghanimat) taqseem nahin farmaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ( Yahya bin abi zaayda ke ilawa) kisi doosrey ne kaha ke Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey wapis kya tha.
2699,(Muhammad bin Suleman al-Anbari ki sanad se marwi (bayan) hai) Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke unka eik ghoda bhag gaya to dushman ne usey pakad liya . phir musalman un par ghalib aagey to wo ghoda Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko wapis dey diya gaya. (eik aur moqe par) Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka eik ghulam bhag gaya aur Rumiyon ke ilaqey mein chala gaya. musalman un par ghalib aaye to Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye unko wapis kar diya. aur ye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baad ka waqia hai.
2700,"Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hudebiya ke roz suleh se pehley kuch ghulam bhag kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aagey to unke malikon ne aap ko likha : aey Muhammad ! (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qasam Allah ki ! ye log tumharey deen ke shoq mein tumharey paas nahin aaye hain, balke ghulami se bhag kar aaye hain. Sahaba mein se kuch ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! unhoney sach kaha hai, aap unhen unko wapis lota den to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghussay huey aur farmaya : ''aey Quraishiyo! main samajhta hun ke tum log us waqt tak baaz nahin aaogey jab tak ke Allah tum par kisi aisey ko na bhej dey jo tumhari us (hatt dharmi) par tumhari gardanen maar dey.'' aur aapney unko wapis kerney se inkar kar diya aur farmaya : ''ye Allah azz-w-jall ke azad karda log hain.''"
2701,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney main eik lashkar ko ghalla aur shehad bataur ghanimat mila , to is mein se khums nahin liya gaya tha."
2702,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke khaibar ke roz charbi se bhara eik thailaa ooper se ludhkaayaa gaya. maine aagey badh kar usey jhapat liya , phir maine kaha : aaj mein is mein se kisi ko kuchh nahin dunga . maine gardan modi to dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri janib (dekh kar) muskura rahey they."
2703,Abu-Labeed bayan kartey hain ke ham Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath mein kaabul mein they. logon ko ghanimat mili to her eik ne usey loot liya . isliye unhoney khutba diya aur farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai ke aapney loot se mana kiya hai. chunanche un logon ne jo kuchh liya tha sab wapis kar diya. phir Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne isey un mein taqseem kar diya.
2704,Muhammad bin Abi Majaalid ne Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya aap log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein khaney peeney ki cheezon mein se khums nikala kartey they? unhoney kaha : hamein khaibar ke roz ghalla mila to zarurat mand aata aur jis qadr usey zarurat hoti lekar chala jata.
2705,Eik Ansari sahabi ne kaha : ham log eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rawana huey. logon ko intehai ehtiyaaj (zaroorat) aur badi mashaqqat ka samna karna pada. unhen bakriyan mil gaeen jo unhoney loot lin (aur taqseem na kin) hamarey degchey ubal rahey they. (gosht pak raha tha) ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni qaus ke saharey chaltey huey tashrif laye aur hamarey degchiyon ko apni Qaus se ulat diya aur gosht ko mitti mein litherne lagey aur farmaya : ''loot ka maal murdar se ziyada halal nahin.'' ya yun farmaya : ''murdar ka gosht loot ke maal se ziyada halal nahin.'' ye shak Hannaad ko hua hai.
2706,"as-haabe Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mein se eik sahabi ka bayan hai, kaha : jihad ke dauran mein ham oont zibeh karkey khatey aur (ba-qaeeda) taqseem na kartey yahan tak ke jab ham wapis laut'tey to hamarey theley is gosht se bharey huey hotey they."
2707,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Ghanam (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke ham ne Hazrat Sharjeel bin Samt (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath mein qinsareen shehar ka muhaasra (gheraaw / gherabandi) kiya. jab unhoney isko Fateh kar liya to wahan se unhen bakriyan aur gayen milen. unhoney in mein se eik hissey ham mein taqseem kar diya aur baqi ko ghanimat mein jama kar liya. phir main ( Abdur-Rehman bin Ghanam) Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se mila aur ye sab unko bataya, to unhoney kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ghazwae khaibar mein shirkat ki, isliye hamein bakriyan milin, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuchh ko ham mein taqseem kar diya (khaney ke liye) aur baqi ko maale ghanimat mein shamil kar liya."
2708,"Hazrat Ruwaifee bin Sabit Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ka Allah par aur qiyamat par emaan hai, usey munasib nahin ke musalmanon ki ghanimat mein se kisi janwar par sawari karta rahey yahan tak ke jab isey laaghir kar daley to isey ghanimat mein wapis kar dey. aur jis ka Allah par aur qiyamat par emaan hai usey jayez nahin ke musalmanon ki ghanimat mein se kapda pehney aur jab usey boseedah kar dey to wo isey is mein wapis kar dey.''"
2709,"Hazrat Abu-Ubaida apney walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke (ghazwae Badr mein) main Abu-Jahal ke paas se guzra. wo gira pada tha aur uski taang par zarab lagi thi. maine us se kaha : aey Allah ke dushman ! aey Abu-Jahal ! (bil-aakhir) Allah ne (tujh) kameeney ko zaleel kar hi diya (ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) kehtey hain ke mujhey us waqt us se koi khauf na tha. to usney kaha : tajjub (aur hasrat) hai us aadmi par ke uski apni hi qom ne usey qatl kar diya to maine usko apni talwaar se maara jo kund si thi aur usney koi faeyda na diya. (usey qatl na kar saki.) lekin uskey haath se uski talwaar gir gaee, tab maine is se usko maara yahan tak ke thanda ho gaya."
2710,Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke khaibar ke roz as-haabe Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mein se eik shakhs wafat pa gaya. logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko iski khabar di to aapney farmaya : ''tum log apney sathi ka janaza padh lo.'' is se logon ke chehrey faq ho gaey . aapney farmaya : ''tumharey is sathi ne Allah ki raah mein hotey huey khayanat (ya chori) ki hai.'' ham ne uskey saman ki talashi li to hamein us mein aisey mungey milin jo yahudi log istimal kartey they (shayad unki aurten istimal karti hon) unki qeemat do dirham bhi na thi.
2711,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ham khaibar ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rawana huey to hamein soney chaandi ki bajaey aam kapdey aur deegar maal aur mataa (daulat) ghanimat mein hasil hua. phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wadi al-quraa ki taraf rawana ho gaey . aap ko eik ghulam hadiya kiya gaya tha jis ka naam Mid'am tha. jab ham wadi al-quraa pahunchey aur Mid'am Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke oont se paalaan utaar raha tha ke usey eik teer aan laga jis se wo qatl ho gaya. logon ne kaha : isey jannat Mubarak ho (ke isey dorane jihad mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat kartey huey maut aai hai) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hargiz nahin, qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! bila-shuba wo chadar jo isney khaibar ke roz taqseem se pehley ghanimat mein se uthai thi wo is par aag bin kar bhadak rahi hai. ''logon ne jab ye suna to koi eik tasma ley aaya to koi do tasmey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke hawaley kar diye. isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik tasma aag ka tha.'' ya farmaya ''do tasmey aag ke they.''"
2712,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab ghanimat hasil hoti to Bilal ko hukm detey aur wo aelan kartey aur log apni apni ghaneematen ley aatey. phir aap is mein se khums (paanchwan hissa) nikaltey aur phir taqseem kar detey. eik baar eik aadmi is aelan aur taqseem ke baad baalon se bani hui eik lagaam ley aaya. usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye hamein ghanimat mein mili thi. aapney us se puchha : ''kya to ne Bilal ko manadi kartey suna tha?'' aapney teen baar poochha. to usney kaha : haan . aapney kaha : ''to (us waqt) tujhey ye ley aaney se kya rukawat thi?'' isney uzr mazrat ki (maafi chahi) magar aapney farmaya : ''ab isey apney paas rakho, qiyamat ke din ley aana, main isey tujh se hergiz qubul nahin karta.''"
2713,"Saleh bin Muhammad bin Zaayda kehtey hain ke main Musallema bin Abdul-Malik ke sath mein romi ilaqey mein gaya to eik aadmi laya gaya jisney ghanimat mein khayanat ki thi. unhoney Salim bin Abdullah bin umr se uskey mutalliq poochha, to unhoney kaha : maine apney walid se suna wo Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey they, aapney farmaya : ''jab tum kisi ko pao ke usney ghanimat mein khayanat ki ho to uska maal aur asbab jala dalo aur usey maaro.'' kehtey hain ke phir ham ne uskey saman mein Quran majeed ka eik nuskha paya. Musallema ne iskey baarey mein Janab Salim se puchha to unhoney kaha : isey farokht karo aur iski qeemat sadqa kar do."
2714,"Saleh bin Muhammad kehtey hain ke ham ne Waleed bin Hisham ke sath mein jihad kiya aur hamarey sath Janab Salim bin Abdullah bin umr aur umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) bhi they. eik shakhs ne ghanimat mein kuchh khayanat kar li. isliye Waleed ne uskey asbab ke mutalliq hukm diya to usey jala diya gaya , phir usey lashkar mein ghumaayaa gaya aur ghanimat ke hissey se bhi usey mehroom kar diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye (mauquf) riwayat pehli ki nisbat ziyada sahih hai. kaee eik ne riwayat kiya hai ke Waleed bin Hisham ne Ziyad bin Saad ka asbab jala diya tha kyonkey usney ghanimat mein khayanat ki thi aur usey maara bhi tha."
2715,"Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ghanimat mein khayanat kerney waley ka maal jalaayaa aur usey maara peetaa. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : Ali bin Bahar ne ba-waaste Waleed mazeed kaha hai : unhoney isey uskey ghanimat ke hissey se mehroom rakha magar main (Abu-Dawud) ne us se ye nahin suna hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : aur hamein ye riwayat Waleed bin Utba aur Abdul-Wahaab bin Najda ne ba-sand Waleed, Zuhair bin Muhammad , Amr bin Shuaib ka apna qaul bataya. aur Abdul-Wahaab bin Najda Hooti ne ghanimat ka hissa na deney ka zikr nahin kiya."
2716,Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( khutbey mein bayan kya ( Amma-Baad ! aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''jisney ghanimat mein kisi khayanat karne wale ki khiyanat par parda dala to wo bhi usi khayanat karne wale ki tarah hai.''
2717,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein Hunain ki taraf rawana huey. jab ham kuffar ke muqabley mein aaye , to musalmanon mein bahut gad-bad machi. maine eik kafir ko dekha ke wo eik musalman par chadhai kar raha tha. mein ghoom kar uskey peechhey se aaya aur uski gardan ke paas talwaar maari, to wo meri taraf aaya aur mujhey (pakad kar) is qadr bheenchaa ke maine is se maut ki boo pai. phir usey maut aa gaee aur usney mujhey chhod diya. main Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se mila aur un se kaha : logon ko kya ho gaya hai? (ke bhag khadey huey hain) unhoney kaha : bas ye Allah ka karna hai. phir log laut aaye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baithey aur farmaya : ''jisney kisi ko qatl kiya ho aur uska gawah bhi ho to us maqtool ka asbab usi ka hai. ''(Abu-Qatada) kehtey hain : main khada hua aur kaha : koi hai jo meri gawahi dey? phir main baith gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dusri baar yehi baat farmaee ke ''jisney kisi ko qatl kiya ho aur uska gawah bhi ho to uska asbab usi ka hai.'' kehtey hain ke main phir utha aur kaha : merey mutalliq gawahi kon deta hai? phir main baith gaya. aapney teesri baar farmaya, to main khada hua , isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne daryaft farmaya : ''Abu-Qatada ! kya baat hai? '' maine apna qissa bayan kiya. to jamaat mein se eik aadmi ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye sach kehta hai aur us maqtool ka asbab merey paas hai. aap isey uskey baarey mein razi farma dijiye. Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : nahin, qasam Allah ki ! (ye nahin ho sakta) ke wo (kafir) Allah ke sheron mein se eik sher ka qasad (iraada) karey jo Allah aur uskey Rasool ki taraf se lad raha ho, aur aap uska salb (asbab) tujhey dey den? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(Abu-Bakar ne) sach kaha. wo asbab isey dey do.'' Abu-Qatada bayan kartey hain : chunanche wo usney mujhey dey diya. phir maine zireh bechi to us se bani Salma main eik baagh kharida. aur wo meri pehli jaaidaad thi jo maine Islam laney ke baad hasil ki."
2718,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hunain waley din farmaya tha : ''jisney kisi kafir ko qatl kiya ho to uska salb (asbab) usi qatil ka hai.'' chunanche Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne isi din bees aadmiyon ko qatl kiya aur unka salb bhi hasil kiya. Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) (apni biwi) Umme-Sulaim se miley jabkey un (Umme-Sulaim) ke paas eik khanjar tha, to puchha : aey Umme-Sulaim ! ye terey paas kya hai? kehney lagin : Allah ki qasam ! mera irada ye hai ke in kafiron mein se koi merey qarib aaya to main is se uska pet cheer dun gi. phir Abu-Talha ne ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bhi batai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : aur is hadees ke bayan se hamara maqsad khanjar ke mutalliq batana hai (ke bataur aslaha uska istimal jayez hai) ke un dino ajmi (gair-arabi) log hi usey istimal kartey they."
2719,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat Zaid bin Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath ghazwae mautaa mein rawana hua. ehale-Yamen se jo kumak hamein mili un mein se eik shakhs merey sath ho liya. uskey paas siwaye eik talwaar ke aur kuchh na tha. musalmanon ke eik aadmi ne oont zibeh kiya, to us aadmi ne zibeh kerney waley se khaal ka eik hissey manga jo usney isko dey diya. isliye usney isko dhaal ki tarah bana liya aur phir ham chaltey rahey. hamein romi jamaaton ka muqabla karna pada. un main eik aadmi apney surkh ghodey par Sawar tha jiski zeen aur hathiyar sunahri they. wo romi musalmanon par badey sakht hamley kar raha tha. to Yamen ki kumak wala ye aadmi eik chattan ki oat mein is romi ki taak mein baith gaya. jab wo iskey paas se guzra to us yamni ne uskey ghodey ki taangein kaat dalin to wo (romi) gir pada aur ye (yamni) khud us aadmi par chadh baitha aur usey qatl kar diya aur uska ghoda aur aslaha ley liya. jab Shan Wale Allah ne musalmanon ko Fateh di to Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne is yamni ko bulwaya aur iskey asbab mein se kuchh ley liya. Hazrat Auf (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main unke paas gaya aur kaha : aey Khalid ! kya aap ko maloom nahin ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka faisla hai ke salb qatil ka hota hai? unhoney kaha : haan. lekin main isey bahut ziyada samajhta hun. maine kaha : ya to aap isey wapis kar den warna main aap ki ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataunga, magar unhoney isko wapis kerney se inkar kar diya. Hazrat Auf (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : phir ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan jama huye, to maine aap se us yamni ka qissa bayan kiya aur wo bhi jo Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kiya tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Khalid ! iski kya wajeh thi jo tum ne kiya?'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine us salb ko bahut ziyada samjha tha. aapney farmaya : ''tum ne jo kuchh us se liya hai wo usko wapis kar do.''  Auf kehtey hain : maine Khalid se kaha : Khalid ! lo ab maine jo baat kahi thi puri kar di? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''wo kya baat hai?'' maine unhen bata di, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghussay ho gaey aur farmaya : ''Khalid ! wo mat wapis karo, kya tum log meri khatir merey Ameeron se koi riayat nahin kar saktey? (ye kaisey ho sakta hai ke) unke maamlat ki umdagi aur bhalai to tumharey liye ho aur uski kharabi ke wo hi zimmedar hon.''"
2720,"Abdur-Rehman bin Jubair bin Nafeer apney walid sey, wo Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) se is hadees ki manind riwayat kartey hain."
2721,Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai aur Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne salb ke mutalliq faisla farmaya ke ye qatil ka haq hai aur us mein se khums nahin nikala.
2722,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Badr ke roz mujhey abu-Jahal ki talwar inayat farmaey. uska kaam unhoney hi tamam kya tha.
2723,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Saeed bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Aban bin Saeed bin Aas ko Madina munawwara se Najad ki janib eik jihaadi muhim par rawana kya. pas Aban bin Saeed aur uskey sathi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas khaibar mein pahunchey jabkey aapney khaibar ko Fateh kar liya tha. Aban bin Saeed aur unke sathiyon ke ghodon ke tang (zeen kasney ke chaudey tasmey, ya lagaam) khajoor ki chhaal ke they. to Aban ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! hamen bhi inayat farmaiye. Hazrat Abu-Huraira kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! unhen mat dijiye. Aban boley : O bille-numa janwer! tum ye keh rahey ho aur (kaha sey) hamarey paas Zaal ( pahad) ki choti se utar aaye ho? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Aban beth jao .'' aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko ghanimat mein se kuch na diya."
2724,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Madiney pahuncha jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khaibar mein they, jis waqt ke aapney usey Fateh kya tha. maine darkhast ki ke aap mujhey bhi inayat farmaeyn. to Saeed bin Aas ke bachon mein se kisi ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! usey mat dijiye. maine kaha : ye ibne-qoqal (Raziallahu anhu) ka qatil hai. to Saeed bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : is billey numa janwer par tajjub hai ke Zaal (pahad) ki choti se hamarey paas utar aaya hai aur mujhey eik musalman ke qatl par aar dilaata hai jis ko Allah azz-w-jall ne merey haathon izzat bakhshi (usey shahadat nasib hui) aur mujhey uskey haathon zaleel nahin kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye log taqriban das aadmi they. unmein se 6 Shahid ho gaey aur baqi wapis lot aaye."
2725,Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham log (Habsha sey) wapis aaye (aur khaibar pahunchey) jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar ko Fateh kar liya tha to aapney ham logon ko bhi hissey diya.....ya kaha ke aapney hamen bhi us mein se kuch diya.... halanke aapney Fateh khaibar se ghayeb rehney walon mein se kisi ko bhi kuch na diya tha. sirf unhi logon ko diya jo aap ke sath hazir they magar ham log jo kashti mein Sawar ho kar aaye they. Hazrat Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke sathiyon ko deegar mujahideen ke sath hissey diya.
2726,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Badr waley din khadey huey aur farmaya : ''Usman (Raziallahu anhu) Allah ke kaam se aur Rasulullah ke kaam se gaey hain aur main unki baiat ley raha hun.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghanimat mein se unka hissey nikala, aur unke siwa ghayeb rehney walon mein se kisi ko kuch nahin diya."
2727,"Yazid bin Hurmuz ne bayan kya ke najda (Haruri, jo ke khawaarij ka sardar tha) ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko kae sawalat likh kar bhejey . un mein se eik ye tha ke kya ghulam ka ghanimat mein koi hissa hota hai? aur aurton ke mutalliq puchha ke kya wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath jihad mein jaya karti thin ? aur kya ghanimat mein unka koi hissa hai ya nahin ? Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne farmaya : agar mujhey ye andesha na hota ke ye koi himaqat kerega to main usey jawab na deta. ( aapney likha ke) ghulam ko inaam diya jata tha, aur aurten zakhmiyon ka ilaj muaalija kya karti thin aur pani pilaya karti thin ."
2728,"Yazid bin Hurmuz ne bayan kya ke Najda Haruri ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko likha aur puchha ke kya aurten Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath jihad mein jaya kartin thin? aur kya aap unhen ghanimat mein se koi hissey inayat farmatey they? Yazid bin Hurmuz kehtey hain : Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka jawab Najda ki taraf maine tehreer kya tha ke aurten Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath jang mein shareek hoten thin aur ye ke unhen ghanimat mein koi hissey diya jaey.....ye nahin hota tha, Taaham unhen Atiya w inaam zarur diya jata tha."
2729,"Hazrat Hashraj bin Ziyad apni daadi (Umme-ziyaad Ashjaia (Raziallahu anha)) se riwayat kartey hain ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ghazwa khaibar mein shareek hui thin aur wo chhe mein se chhati aurat thi, kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khabar hui to aapney hamen bulwa bheja. ham hazire-khidmat huin to hamne aap ko ghussey mein dekha. farmaya : ''tum kiske sath aur kiski ijazat se aai ho?'' ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! ham aai hain baal bat-ti hain, aur us se jihad mein madad karti hain, hamarey paas zakhmiyon ke liye dawa-daru bhi hai, ham teer ikhattey karkey deti hain aur sattu pilaati hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jao.'' (koi baat nahin) yahan tak ke jab Allah ne aap ke liye khaibar Fateh kar diya to aapney hamen bhi hissey inayat farmaya jaisey ke mardon ko diya tha. maine puchha daadi amman! wo kya tha? kaha : khajoor."
2730,"Hazrat Umair (Raziallahu anhu) jo ke Hazrat Aabi Leham (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghulam they, bayan kartey hain ke main apney malikon ke sath ghazwa khaibar mein hazir hua to unhoney merey mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se baat ki, to aapney merey mutalliq hukm diya, meri gardan main eik talwaar latka di gaee, main usey ghaseetney laga. phir aapko bataya gaya ke ye ghulam hai to aapney merey mutalliq farmaya aur mujhey ghar ke asbab mein se kuch bator inaam diya gaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : iskey maani ye hain ke aapney ghanimat mein se hissey nahin diya tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha hai : abu-Ubaid ne bayan kya ke raawi hadees ''Aabi Leham'' ki wajeh tasmiya ye hai ke unhoney gosht ko apney liye haram kar liya tha isliye unhen ''Aabi leham'' kaha jata tha (gosht se inkar kerney wala.)"
2731,Hazrat Jabir (bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma)) ka bayan hai ke main Badr ke roz apney as-haab ke liye kunwen se pani bharta raha tha. (kunwen mein utar kar haathon se dol bharta tha kyonkey nichey pani kam tha.)
2732,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke mushrekin mein se eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mila , taake aap ke sath mil kar (mushrekin sey) qitaal karey. aapney farmaya : ''wapis chaley jao.'' (ye alfaz Yahya bin Mueen ke hain. uskey baad Musaddad aur Yahya dono ittifaq key sath kehtey hain ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ham mushrekin se madad nahin letey.''"
2733,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Mujahid aur uskey ghodey ke liye teen hissey muqarrar farmaai they. eik hissey Mujahid ka aur do hissey uskey ghodey ke .
2734,Hazrat Abu-Umra apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey ham chaar aadmi they aur hamarey paas ghoda tha to aapney ham mein se her eik ko eik-eik hissey aur ghodey ko do hissey inayat farmaey.
2735,(Janab Musaddad ki sanad se hai ke) Abu-Umra ne mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya magar is riwayat mein hai ke ham teen log aaye aur aapney ghud-Sawar ko teen hissey inayat farmaey.
2736,"Hazrat Majma-bin-Jariya Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai.....aur ye aisey qaari they jinhone pura Quran padha tha, (hifz kya tha)..... wo bayan kartey hain : ham Hudebiya mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath hazir they. jab ham wahan se wapis honey lagey to dekha ke log apney oonton ko tez bhaga rahey hain, logon ne eik doosrey se puchha : kya baat hai? unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par wahi nazil hui hai, to ham bhi logon ke sath oont daudaatey huey nikley . ham ne Kura-al-Ghamim maqam par dekha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni sawari par rukey huey hain. jab log aap ke paas jama ho gaey to aapney sura Fateh ki aayaat tilawat farmaeyn : ( إنا فتحنا لك فتحا مبينا ( ''bila-shuba ham ne aap ko wazeh Fateh di hai.'' eik shakhs ne puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya ye Fateh hai? farmaya : ''haan, us zaat ki qasam jiskey haath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai! bila-shuba ye Fateh hai. ''chunanche (baad mein) khaibar ki ghaneematein ehle-Hudebiya hi par taqseem ki gaeen. aapney unke atthaara hissey banaey aur lashkar walon ki tadaad pandarah so thi jin mein teen so ghud-Sawar they. pas aapney ghud-Sawar ko do hissey aur pedal ko eik hissey inayat farmaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : abu-Muaawia ki hadees ziyada sahih hai aur usi par amal hai. (hadees 2733) aur majme ki riwayat mein weham hai ke ye ghud-Sawar teen so batatey hain halanke wo do so they."
2737,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Badr ke din farmaya : '' jisney aisey-aisay kya usey itna-itna inaam (nafl) milega.'' chunanche nojawan aagey badhey aur badi umr ke log nishaanat (ya jhandon) ke paas rukey rahey. jab Allah taala ne unko Fateh di to buzurgon ne kaha : ham tumhara sahara they agar tumhen shikast hoti to tum log hamarey hi paas lot ke aatey , sari ghanimat tum hi na samet ley jao ke hamen kuch na miley magar jawaanon ne inkar kya aur kehney lagey : ye to wo chiz hai jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamarey liye makhsus farmaai hai. tab Allah taala ne sura Anfal ki aayaat nazil farmaeyn : (يسألونك an الأنفال قل الأنفال لله والرسول) se lekar :  (و إن فريقا من المؤمنين لكارهون) chunanche ye sab unke liye behtar hua aur aisey farmaya ke meri itaat karo, be-shak uskey anjam ko mein tum se behtar janta hun."
2738,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Badr ke din farmaya : ''jisney kisi ko qatl kya to uskey liye itna itna inam hai aur jo kisi ko pakad kar qaid kar ley to uskey liye itna-itna hai.'' phir mazkura baala hadees ki manind bayan kya aur Khalid ki hadees ziyada kamil hai.
2739,"(Harun bin Muhammad bin Bakkar ki sanad se marwi (bayan) hai) aur Dawud bin abi Hind ne ye hadees apni sanad se riwayat ki hai, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghanimat ko barabar barabar taqseem kya. aur Khalid ki riwayat ziyada kamil hai. (mazkura baala hadees : 2737 ( ."
2740,"Hazrat Musab bin Saad apney walid (Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain unhoney bayan kya ke Badr ke roz main eik talwaar lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Allah taala ne aaj dushman ke muqabley mein mera seena thanda kar diya hai, to aap ye talwaar mujhey inayat farma dijiye . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye talwaar na meri hai aur na teri .'' chunanche main chala aur main keh raha tha : ye aaj us aadmi ko de-di jaeygi jisney merey jaisi bahaduri nahin dikhai hogi . main isi keyfiyat mein tha ke eik bulaney wala merey paas aaya aur kaha ke (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan) pahuncho. maine guman kya ke maine jo bol boley hain unki bina par merey baarey mein koi wahi nazil hui hogi. chunanche main aaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya '' to ne mujh se ye talwaar maangi thi, halanke ye na meri hai na teri aur (ab) Allah azz-w-jall ne isey mujhey dey diya hai, so ( ab ( ye teri hai. '' phir aapney sura Anfal ki ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ( يسألونك an الأنفال قل الأنفال لله والرسول ( aakhir aayat tak . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki qirat mein hai : '' ( يسألونك النفل ( '' ( baghair an (an) ke aur mufrad seegha ke sath ("
2741,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen eik lashkar mein Najad ki taraf rawana kya aur us mein se eik dasta dushman ke muqabley mein gaya. chunanche lashkar walon ko 12-12 oont miley lekin us dastey mein shareek mujaahidon ko eik eik oont mazeed diya gaya , is tarah unka hissey 13-13 oont ho gaya."
2742,"Waleed bin Utba dimashqi kehtey hain ke Waleed bin Muslim ne kaha : maine ibne-mubarak se ye hadees bayan ki . maine kaha : hamen ibne-abi farwa ne bhi Naafe se ye riwayat bayan ki hai. ibne-Mubarak ne kaha : ye log, jinka tum ne naam liya hai, Malik bin Anas ke barabar nahin ho saktey. (Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) ki riwayat rajeh hai)"
2743,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik dasta Najad ki janib rawana kya, main bhi unke sath tha. hamen bahut se janwer haath aaye to hamarey ameer ne ham mein se her her shakhs ko eik eik oont bator nafl diya. phir ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas pahunchey aur aapney ham mein hamari ghanimatein taqseem kin to ham mein se her-her shakhs ko khums nikalney ke baad 12-12 oont miley aur hamarey ameer ne jo hamen diya tha uska Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne koi muhaasba na farmaya aur na uski karrawai par koi aeb lagaya, is tarah hamen nafl samet 13-13 oont miley ."
2744,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik dasta Najad ki taraf rawana farmaya jis mein Abdullah bin umr bhi shamil they. to un logon ko bahut badi tadaad mein oont hasil huey . chunanche lashkar ke mujahideen ka hissa 12-12 oont hua aur eik eik oont bator nafl mazeed diye gaey . ibn mohab ne mazeed kaha ke) ameer ki taqseem mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne koi tabdeeli na farmaai.
2745,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen eik dastey mein rawana kya to hamarey hissey mein baara baara oont aaye . aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen eik eik oont mazeed bator nafl inayat farmaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is riwayat ko Burd bin Sanan ne b-waasta Naafe, Ubaidullah ki hadees ki manind riwayat kya hai. aur Ayub ne bhi Naafe se usi tarah riwayat kya hai magar us riwayat mein hai ke '' hamen eik eik oont bator nafl diya gaya .'' us mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka zikr nahin hai."
2746,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( badey lashkar mein sey) jab chhotey daston ko bhejtey to un logon ko aam lashkar mein taqseem honey wali ghanimat ke ilawa khas nafl (izafi inaam) bhi diya kartey they. aur khums majmui ghanimat mein se nikalna wajib hai.
2747,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Badr ke roz 315 logon ko lekar rawana huey . aapney dua farmaai : ''aey Allah ! ye log pedal hain, inhen sawariyan dey, aey Allah ! ye log be libas hain, inhen libas inayat farma , aey Allah ! bhookey hain inhen sair farma.'' chunanche Allah taala ne aap ko Badr mein Fateh inayat farmaai. pas jab ye log wapis huey to un mein se her eik ke paas eik-eik ya do-do oont they, unhen kapdey bhi miley aur khaney se bhi sair huey ."
2748,Hazrat Habib bin Muslima Fahri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ghanimat mein sey) paanchwan hissey nikalney ke baad teesra hissey nafl yani izafi inaam ke taur par taqseem farmaya kartey they.
2749,Hazrat Habib bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khums nikalney ke baad shuru mein) pehli martaba ( chotha hissey bator nafl (izafi inaam) diya kartey they. aur ghazwey se laut-tey waqt ( dobara lashkar kushi mein) teesra hissey diya kartey they khums nikal leney ke baad .
2750,"Hazrat Mak-hool ( Shami (Rahimahullah) ( bayan kartey hain ke main Misr mein bani-Huzail ki eik aurat ka ghulam tha. usney mujhey azad kar diya. phir main wahan ( Misr ( se us waqt tak nahin nikla jab tak ke apni daanist ke mutabiq wahan ke ulama se tamam ka tamam ilm hasil nahin kar liya. phir main hijaaz aaya aur wahan se us waqt tak nahin nikla jab tak ke apni daanist ke mutabiq wahan ka tamam ilm jama nahin kar liya. phir Iraq aaya aur wahan se us waqt tak nahin nikla jab tak ke apni daanist ke mutabiq wahan ka tamam ilm jama nahin kar liya. phir main shaam aaya aur us (ke ulama) ko khoob kureda aur her eik se main ghanimat mein nafl ( izafi inaam (ke mutalliq sawal karta raha to mujhey koi na mila jo mujhey is baarey mein kuch batata. bil-aakhir main eik Shekh se mila jiska naam Ziyad bin jaariya tamimi tha, maine us se puchha : kya aapney nafl ke mutalliq kuch suna hai? usney kaha : haan ! maine Habib bin Muslima fahri (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna hai, farma rahey they : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan hazir tha ke aapney shuru jihad mein chotha hissey aur laut-tey waqt (dusri baar hamla kerney ki soorat mein) teesra hissey bator nafl ( izafi inaam ( inayat farmaya tha."
2751,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo ( Shuaib ( apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sab musalmanon ke khoon aapas mein barabar hain. (sazaon ke laagu honey mein muazzaz aur ghair muazzaz ka koi farq nahin) un mein se jo bhi kisi kafir ko aman dey dey to unka adna fard bhi uska paas rakhey (jaisey ke aalaa rakhtey hain) aur un mein ka door wala bhi aman dey sakta hai (jaisey ke markaz mein rehney wala) tamam musalman kuffar ke muqabley main eik haath hain, unka mota-taaza aur qawi raftaar apney zaeef aur sust-raftar ko bhi sath milaaey aur chhotey dastey mein janey wala badey lashkar mein reh janey walon ko bhi shareek samjhey, kisi momin ko kafir ke badley mein ya kisi ehad waley ko jab tak ke uska ehad baqi ho qatl karna munasib nahin.'' ibne-Is-haq ne apni riwayat mein qisaas aur khoon barabar honey ka zikr nahin kya."
2752,"Ayas bin Salma apney walid ( Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke Abdur-Rehman bin Uena (fazari) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke oont loot liye , unke charwaahey ko qatl kar dala aur phir wo aur uskey ghud-Sawar sathi unhen haanktey huey chal nikley .) mujhey khabar hui ( to maine apna munh Madina ki taraf kya aur teen baar ye haank lagai : (يا صبا حاه) ! (logo! madad ko pahuncho, ham ko dushman ne loot liya hai) phir main (dodtey huey ( un logon ke peechey ho liya , teer maarta jata tha aur unki sawaariyon ko zakhmi karta ja raha tha, agar un mein se koi ghud-Sawar meri taraf palat-ta to main kisi darkht ki ot mein ho jata yahan tak ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki tamam sawariyan jo Allah ne paida farmaai thin maine unko apney peechey (apney qabzey mein) kar liya . aur un logon ne apna bojh halka kerney ki gharz se tees se ziyada bhaale aur tees chadaren phenk din. phir Uena bhi unki madad ko aan pahuncha to usney kaha : tum mein se kuch aadmi us (Salma bin Akwa) ki taraf ho jao. to un mein se chaar aadmi meri taraf aaye aur pahad par chadh gaey. maine buland aawaz se unhen kaha : kya tum mujhey pehchaantey ho? unhoney poochha, tum kon ho? maine kaha : main akwaa ka farzand hun, us zaat ki qasam jisney Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke chehrey ko izzat bakhshi hai! ye nahin ho sakta ke tum mein se koi mujhey pakadna chahey to main uskey haath aa jaun aur agar main pakadna chahun to wo bhag nikley. phir thodi der guzri to maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke shehsawaar darakhton mein se (dodey) aa rahey hain. un mein sab se aagey Hazrat Akhram Asadi (Raziallahu anhu) they. wo Abdur-Rehman bin Uena ke muqabley mein ho gaey, Abdur-Rehman un par palta aur phir dono ne eik doosrey par neze chillaey . chunanche Akhram Asadii (Raziallahu anhu) ne us ( Abdur-Rehman (ka ghoda zakhmi kar diya aur Abdur-Rehman ne Akhram (Raziallahu anhu) ko neza maara aur unko Shahid kar diya. phir Abdur-Rehman, Akhram (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghodey par Sawar ho gaya to abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) Abdur-Rehman ke muqabley mein aagey. unke beech bhi neze ke hamlon ka tabaadla hua. usney abu-Qatada ka ghoda zakhmi kar diya lekin abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abdur-Rehman ko qatl kar dala. phir abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) Akhram (Raziallahu anhu) waley ghodey par Sawar ho gaey. phir main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabke aap us chashmey par tashrif ley aaye they jahan se maine unko bhagaya tha. uska naam Zu-qard tha. maine dekha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) paanch so Sawar liye huey they. pas aapney mujhey eik shehsawar aur eik pedal ka hissa inayat farmaya."
2753,"Hazrat Abu-Juweriya jurmi (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ameer Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke daur mein mujhey Rumi ilaqey mein surkh rang ka eik ghada mila, us mein Dinar they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke as-haab mein se bani-Sulaim ke eik fard Hazrat maan bin Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey ameer they, wo ghada mein unke paas ley aaya. pas unhoney usey musalmanon mein taqsim kar diya aur mujhey bhi itna hi diya jitna ke doosron mein se her eik ko diya. phir kaha : agar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey na suna hota ke ''izafi inam (nafl) khums nikalney ke baad hi ho sakta hai.'' to main tumhen bhi deta, phir wo apna hissey mujhey deney ki koshish kartey rahey magar maine inkar kar diya."
2754,(pasand Hannad) Aasim bin Kulaib ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya.
2755,"Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen Namaz padhaai, ghanimat ka eik oont (bator sutrah) aagey tha, jab aapney salam phera to aapney us oont ke pehlu se kuch baal liye phir farmaya : ''aur tumhari ghaneematon mein se merey liye is qadr bhi halal nahin siwaye paanchwen hissey ke, aur wo paanchwan hissey bhi phir tum hi mein wapis ho jata hai.''"
2756,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(ehad w peman mein) dhoka kerney waley ke liye qiyamat ke roz eik jhanda gaada jaeyga aur kaha jaeyga : ye falan bin falan ka dhoka hai.''"
2757,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Imam dhaal hai ke uskey sath qitaal kya jata hai.''"
2758,"Hazrat abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke (suleh Hudebiya ke moqe par) Qureshiyon ne mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf rawana kya. jab maine aap ko dekha to merey dil mein Islam ki raghbat dal di gaee, pas maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! main to Allah ki qasam kabhi bhi ab unki taraf nahin jaunga. aapney farmaya : ''main ehad ko nahin todta aur na qaasidon ko qaid karta hun, tumhen chahiye ke wapis jao, agar tumharey dil mein wohi baat rahey jo ab hai to wapis aa jana.'' kehtey hain : main wapis gaya, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein lot aaya aur Islam qubul kar liya. Buker kehtey hain : mujhey (Hasan bin Ali ne) bataya ke (uska dada) abu-Raafe qibti ghulam tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye us zamaney mein tha (ke qaasid musalman hona chaha raha tha to usey wapis kar diya) aaj durust nahin hai."
2759,"Hazrat Salim bin Aamir (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai aur ye qabeela Himyar se they, wo bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) aur Rumiyon ke darmiyan muahida (suleh w aman) ho chuka tha aur (Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) un dinon muahida mein) unke ilaqon ki taraf kooch kar rahey they taake junhi muahidey ki muddat khatam ho (achanak) un par chadhai kar den, to arbi ghodey ya turkii ghodey par Sawar eik shakhs unki taraf aaya . wo : ( الله اكبر , الله اكبر ( wafadari ho, ghadr nahin, pukarta aa raha tha. logon ne dekha to wo sahabi Rasool Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) they. Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen bulwaaya aur poochha, to unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna hai : ''jiska dusri qom se koi muahida ho to wo us waqt tak koi naya muahida na karey aur na usey khatam karey jab tak ke pehley muahidey ki muddat baqi ho ya barabari ki sateh par usey todney ka aelan kar dey.'' chunanche Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) lot aaye."
2760,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney kisi ehad waley ko baghair kisi wajeh jawaz ke qatl kya to Allah ne us par jannat haram kar di.''"
2761,"Muhammad bin Is-haq ki riwayat hai ke Musailma (kazzaab) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf khat bheja. (doosri sanad mein hai) Nueim-bin-Masood Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aapney Musailma ke do elchiyon se puchha jabkey aapney (us kazaab ka ( khat padha ke ''tum dono (uskey baarey mein) kya kehtey ho?'' unhoney kaha : ham wohi kehtey hain jo usney kaha hai. aapney farmaya : ''Allah ki qasam! agar ye baat na hoti ke safeer aur qaasidon ko qatl nahin kya jata, to main tum dono ki gardanen uda deta.''"
2762,"Harisa bin Muzrib (Rahimahullah) se manqul hai ke wo Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye (jabkey wo koofa mein waali they) aur kaha : mujhey kisi arab se koi adawat nahin aur main qabeela banu-Hanifa ki masjid se guzra hun to maine unhen paya hai ke wo log Musailma par emaan rakhtey hain (ye masjid koofa hi mein thi.) pas Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen bulwa liya, unhen laya gaya to unhoney (Abdullah bin Masood ne) un se tauba karwaai, siwaye ibn nawaaha ke, Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai ke aapney (tujh sey) kaha tha : ''agar to safeer na hota to main teri gardan uda deta.'' aur aaj to safeer ya qaasid nahin hai. chunanche unhoney Qarza bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya to unhoney usko baazar mein (sare-aam) qatl kar diya. phir farmaya : jo ibn nawaaha ko maqtool dekhna chahta hai wo usey baazar mein dekh ley."
2763,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke usey Umme- Hani binte-abi Talib (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke usney Fateh Makka ke roz eik mushrik ko panah di thi. phir wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai aur ye waqia bayan kya to aapney us se farmaya : ''ham ne panah di usey jisko to ne panah di. ham ne aman di usey jisko to ne aman di.''
2764,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke (daure-risaalat mein) aurat kisi ko mominon se panah dey deti to wo jayez aur qubul hua karti thi (musalman usey qatl na kar saktey they.)
2765,"Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hudebiya ke moqe par chaudah , pandarah so Sahaba ke sath mein rawana huey . (1) jab zal-Hulaifa pahunchey to aapney apni qurbani ko Qalada pehnaya aur uskey kohan par cheer lagaya (ashaar kya) aur Umerey ka ehram baandha. (2) aur hadees bayan ki. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rawana huey yahan tak ke jab us ghaati par pahunchey jahan se ehle-Makka ki taraf utartey hain to aap ki sawari beth gaee. logon ne kaha : ( hal hal ( ) oont ko uthaney ki aawaz hai) qaswa bigad gaee hai (ya ad gaee hai) do baar kaha : (3) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye na bigdi hai aur na uski ye aadat hai, usey haathi ko rokney waley ne roka hai.'' (4) phir farmaya : ''qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! ye log aaj mujhey jo bhi koi aisi tajweez pesh karengey jis se wo Allah ki hurmaton ki tazeem baja laeyn to main usey qubul kar lunga.'' (5) phir aapney oontni ko daanta to wo jaldi se uth khadi hui. phir aapney unki taraf se raasta tabdeel kar liya yahan tak ke Hudebiya ke paar eik kunwen par ja utrey, us mein pani bahut thoda tha. phir aap ke paas budail bin Warqa Khuzaae aaya. (6) uskey baad Urwa bin Masood aaya aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se guftgu kerney laga. wo jab bhi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se baat karta to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki dadhi Mubarak par haath pherta. (7) Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke sath hi khadey they (8) unke haath mein talwaar aur sar par khod thi, (Urwa aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se baat kartey huey aap ki dadhi par haath lagata to) wo apni talwaar ka dasta uskey haath par dey maartay aur kehtey : door kar apna haath unki dadhi se. Urwa ne apna sar uthaya aur puchha ye kon hai? haazirin ne kaha : ye Mughira-bin-Shoba hain to wo bola : aey dhoke-baaz! kya main terey dhokey aur fasad mein suleh safai nahin karata raha hun? (darasal) Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) Islam se pehley kuch logon ke sath they to unko qatl kar diya, unke maal loot liye, phir ja kar Islam qubul kar liya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Islam to ham ne qubul kar liya magar maal chunkey dhokey ka hai isliye hamen uski koi zarurat nahin.'' (9) aur hadees bayan ki. chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' likho ye wo ( ehad nama ( hai jis par Muhammad Rasulullah ne ittifaq kya hai. '' aur pura qissa bayan kya. ( 10 ( Suhel ne kaha . ... aur ham mein se jo koi bhi aap ke paas aaye chahey wo aap ke deen hi par kyon na ho wo aap ko hamari taraf wapis karna hoga. phir jab ehad namey ki tehreer se farigh ho gaey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney Sahaba se farmaya : '' utho ! qurbaniyan karo aur apney sar moond lo .'' phir momin aur Muhajir aurten aain (to Allah taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaai: ''aey emaan walo ! jab tumharey paas momin aurten hijrat karkey ayen . . . . Mumtahina : 60 / 10 ( tu Allah taala ne hukm diya ke unhen wapis nahin lautana, albatta ye hukm diya ke unke haq mehar wapis kar diye jaeyn . phir aap Madina wapis tashrif ley aaye . Quraish ka eik aadmi Abu-Baseer , aap ke paas aa gaya. to un logon ne usko leney ke liye apney do aadmi bhej diye . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey unke hawaley kar diya. wo usey lekar chaley gaey yahan tak ke jab zul-Hulaifa maqam par pahunchey to unhoney wahan padaaw kya aur apni khajuren khaney lagey. Abu-Baseer ne un mein se eik ko kaha : aray! teri ye talwaar to bahut umda dikhai deti hai. usney usey miyaan se nikala aur kaha : han! han! maine usko bahut aazmaya hai. Abu-Baseer ne kaha : dikhaana zara, main usey dekhun to sahi. aur wo usney usko pakda di. pas Abu-Baseer ne wo usey dey maari yahan tak ke wo thanda ho gaya. aur uskey sath wala doosra aadmi bhag kar Madiney aa gaya aur bhagtey bhagtey masjid mein chala aaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(ye khof-zada hai.) usney koi khofnak chiz dekhi hai. '' wo bola : Allah ki qasam! mera sathi qatl kar diya gaya hai aur main bhi maara janey wala hun. phir Abu-Baseer bhi aa gaya to usney kaha : Allah ne aap ki zimmedari puri kara di ke aapney mujhey unke hawaley kar diya tha, phir Allah ne mujhey un se najat de-di hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uski maa ka afsos! ye to jang ki aag bhadkaane wala hai agar koi usey mil jaey.'' jab usney ye suna to samajh gaya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey un logon ki taraf lota dengey . so wo wahan se nikal khada hua aur sahil samandar par aa gaya. phir abu-jandal bhi nikal bhaaga aur Abu-Baseer ke sath ja mila yahan tak ke wahan eik jamaat ikhatti ho gaee."
2766,"Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima aur Marwan bin Hakam se manqul hai ke Quraish ne is baat par suleh ki ke das saal tak koi jang nahin hogi log us muddat mein her tarah aman se rahengey, (us muahidey ke mutalliq) ham dono fariqon ke dil saaf rahengey, chori chupey ya khayanat se uski mukhalifat na hogi ."
2767,"Khalid bin Maadaan ne bayan kya ke Jubair bin Nafair ne kaha ke aaiye ham Janab zi-Mukhbir (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas chaltey hain wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sahabi they. to ham unke paas gaey . Jubair ne un se suleh ke mutalliq puchha , to unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai aap farmatey they : ''tum log Rumiyon se eik pur-amn suleh karogey aur phir tum aur wo apney peechey ( kisi ( eik dushman se qitaal karogey.''"
2768,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kon hai jo Kab bin ashraf ki khabar ley ? bila-shuba usney Allah aur uskey Rasool ko aziyat di hai. '' pas Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main hazir hun. kya aap chahtey hain ke main usey qatl kar dalun? aapney farmaya : ''han!'' unhoney kaha : mujhey ijazat dijiye ke main uskey samney koi baat bana sakun. aapney farmaya : ''han! tum keh saktey ho.'' chunanche Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) uskey paas gaey aur kaha : us aadmi ne ham se sadqaat talab kiye hain aur hamen bahut tang kar rakha hai. usney kaha : abhi tum us shakhs se aur bhi ukta jaogey. ibne-Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : chunkey ham uski perwi ikhtiyar kar chukey hain isliye fauran usey chhod dena munasib nahin hai yahan tak ke dekh lein ke uska anjam kya hota hai. ham chahtey hain ke tum hamen eik do wasq ( ghalla waghera) dey do . Kab ne kaha : bator rehen kya chiz dogey ? unhoney kaha : tum ham se kya chahtey ho? usney kaha : apni aurten dey do . unhoney kaha : Subhanallah ! tum arab ke Husain tareen shakhs ho, ham tumhen apni aurten bator rehan dey den, to ye hamarey liye bahut badi aar hogi. wo bola : chalo apni auladen dey do. unhoney kaha : Subhanallah ! (sari zindagi) hamarey bachey ko ye gaali di jati rahegi ke tumhen to eik ya do wasq ke badley mein rehan rakha gaya tha. unhoney kaha : haan ham apna aslaha bator rehan dey saktey hain. to wo bola : haan theek hai. chunanche wo log jab uskey paas aaye to ibn Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko aawaz di, wo bahir aaya, usney khushbu laga rakhi thi aur uska sar khushbu se mehak raha tha. pas jab wo uskey paas beth gaya. aur Muhammad bin Muslima apney sath teen ya chaar sathiyon ko bhi laye they. sab ne us se khushbu ka tazkira kya. wo kehney laga : merey yahan falan aurat hai jo behtareen khushbu wali aurat hai. ibn Muslima ne kaha : agar ijazat do to main soongh lun. usney kaha : han! han! pas unhoney apna haath uskey sar mein kya aur usey sungha. unhoney kaha : zara eik baar phir. usney kaha : han! han! to unhoney apna haath uskey sar mein dala aur uskey baalon ko khoob jakad liya aur apney sathiyon se kaha : lo apna kaam karo, to unhoney usko maara yahan tak ke qatl kar dala ."
2769,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eman ne dhokey se qatl kerney ko band kar diya hai, koi sahab eman dhokey se qatl nahin kar sakta.''"
2770,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi ghazwey, hajj ya Umerey (ke safar) se wapis aatey huey zameen ki kisi bhi bulandi par chadhtey, to teen baar ( الله اكبر ( kehtey aur ye dua padhtey : لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له ، له الملك وله الحمد وهو على كل شيء قدير ، آيبون تائبون عابدون ساجدون لربنا حامدون ، صدق الله وعده ، ونصر عبده ، وهزم الأحزاب وحده''Allah ke siwa koi mabud nahin wo eik hai uska koi shareek nahin, usi ki hukoomat hai, tamam tarah ki tareefen usi ki hain aur wo her chiz par kamil qudrat rakhta hai. ham lotney waley hain, tauba kerney waley hain, ibadat kerney waley hain, sajda kerney waley hain aur apney rab ki hamd kerney waley hain, Allah ne apna wada sach kar dikhaya, apney bandey ki nusrat farmaai aur tamam girohon ko us akeley hi ne paspa kar diya. ''"
2771,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke sura tauba ki aayat kareema : (لا يستأذنك الذين يؤمنون بالله واليوم الآخر . . ۔) ko sura Noor ki aayat kareema : (إنما المؤمنون الذين آمنوا بالله ورسوله ) ne mansookh kar diya hai.
2772,"Hazrat Jarir (bin Abdullah Al Bajli) (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : ''kya tum mujhey zi-khalsa se rahat nahin pahuncha saktey?'' chunanche wo iskey paas aaye aur isko jala dala, phir qabeela Ahmas ka eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf bheja , jo aap ke paas khushkhabri lekar gaya. uski kunniyat Abu-Irtaa thi."
2773,"Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab bhi kisi safar se wapis laut'tey to sab se pehley masjid mein tashrif ley jatey, wahan do rakaten padhtey aur phir logon se milney ke liye baith jatey. (Imam Abu-Dawud ke shaikh) ibne Sarah ne puri hadees bayan ki aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne musalmanon ko mana farma diya tha ke ham teeno se koi baat cheet karey. yahan tak ke jab ye kaifiyat bahut taweel ho gaee to main apney chacha zaad Abu-Qatada ki deewar par chadha aur maine usko salam kaha. Allah ki qasam ! usney mujhey jawab nahin diya. phir jab pachas raaten puri ho gaeen aur us subh Fajr ki Namaz maine apney eik makaan ki chhat par padhi, to maine eik buland aawaz se pukarney waley ki aawaz suni jo keh raha tha : aey Kab bin Malik ! khushkhabri ho. phir jab wo merey paas pahuncha, jiski aawaz maine suni thi, to maine uskey liye apney kapdey utarey aur usko pehna diye. phir main chala yahan tak ke jab masjid mein dakhil hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif farma they. Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) daudtey huey meri taraf lapkey, yahan tak ke mujh se musaafa kiya aur mubarak-baad pesh ki."
2774,Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jab koi khushi ki khabar aati ya aap ko bashaarat di jati to aap Allah ka shukr kartey huey sajdey mein gir jatey they.
2775,"Hazrat Aamir bin Saad apney walid ( Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) se bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath main Makka se rawana huey, hamara irada Madiney janey ka tha. jab ham maqame-Azdara ke qarib pahunchey to aap apni sawari se utar padey. phir apney dono haath uthaey aur eik ghadi Allah se dua kartey rahey. phir sajdey mein gir gaey aur der tak sajdey mein padey rahey. phir uthey, apney dono haath uthaey aur eik ghadi Allah se dua kartey rahey, phir sajdey mein gir gaey aur badi der tak sajdey mein padey rahey, phir uthey aur apney dono haath buland kiye aur eik ghadi tak buland kiye rakhey, phir sajdey mein gir gaey . ... . Ahmed bin Saleh ne ye amal teen baar ka bayan kiya. ... farmaya : ''maine apney Rab se sawal kiya hai aur apni ummat ke liye shafaat ki hai. isliye Allah ne mujhey meri ummat ka tihai hissey dey diya (usey bakhsh dunga), to main apney Rab ka shukr kartey huey sajdey mein gir gaya. phir maine apna sar uthaya , apney Rab se apni ummat ke liye dua ki to usney mujhey meri ummat ka (mazeed) tihai hissey inayat farma diya to main apney Rab ka shukr kartey huey sajdey mein gir gaya. phir maine sar uthaya , apney Rab se apni ummat ke liye sawal kiya to usney mujhey meri ummat ka mazeed tihai hissey bhi dey diya to main apney Rab ke liye sajdey mein gir gaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : merey shaikh Ahmed bin Saleh ne jab ye sanad bayan ki to is mein se Ash'as bin Is'haq ka unhoney zikr nahin kiya. uska zikr Musa bin Sehal Ramli ne kiya hai."
2776,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is baat ko napasand farmatey they ke insan raat ke waqt apney ghar pahunchey .
2777,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' safar se wapsi ke moqe par ghar walon ke paas aaney ka behtareen waqt raat ka pehla hissa hota hai. ''"
2778,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke ham eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they. jab ( ham Madiney ke qarib aakhiri padaaw par they ( ham ne chaha ke gharon ko jaeyn , to aapney farmaya : '' zara thehro, raat ho ley to jaeyn taake paraganda haal khatoon kanghi choti kar ley aur jiska shohar ghayeb tha wo apney (zere-naaf) baalon ki safai kar ley . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Imam Zohri (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : '' ( الطروق ( '' Isha ke baad aaney ko kehtey hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : maghrib ke baad aaney mein koi harj nahin."
2779,Hazrat Saaib bin Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ghazwa tabuk se Madina tashrif laye to logon ne aap ka istaqbal kya. doosrey bachon ke sath maine bhi saniya al-wada ke maqam par aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka istaqbal kya tha.
2780,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke qabeela Aslam ka eik nojawan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main jihad ke liye jana chahta hun magar tayyari ke liye merey paas koi maal nahin hai. aapney farmaya : '' falan Ansari ke yahan chaley jao, usney tayyari kar rakhi thi magar bimar ho gaya hai. to usey kaho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) salam kehtey hain aur farmatey hain : jo samane-safar tum ne tayyar kar rakha tha wo mujhey dey do .'' chunanche wo unke paas gaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka pegham diya. to usney apni biwi se kaha : aey falani! jo saman to ney merey liye tayyar kya tha wo us shakhs ke hawaley kar dey aur us mein se kuch bhi na rakhna , Allah ki qasam ! agar to ney us mein se koi chiz rakh li tu Allah us mein barkat nahin dega."
2781,"Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) safar se wapis tashrif latey to ( aam taur se ( din hi mein aaya kartey they. (raawi hadees) Hasan bin Ali ne kaha ke chaasht ke waqt aaya kartey they. aur jab safar se ( wapis ( aatey to masjid mein tashrif ley jatey , wahan do rakatein padhtey phir wahan beth jatey (taake logon se mulaqat kar lein .)"
2782,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab apney hajj se wapis tashrif laye aur Madiney mein dakhil huey to apni oontni ko masjid ke darwazey ke paas bithaya aur masjid mein chaley gaey aur do rakatein ada kin phir apney ghar tashrif ley gaey. Naafe bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bhi aisey hi kya kartey they.
2783,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qasama (taqseem kerney ki ujrat) se bacho.'' ham ne arz kya : ''qasama'' se kya murad hai? aapney farmaya : ''koi chiz logon mein mushtarak ho aur koi aaye aur us mein se (apney liye) kuch nikal ley.''"
2784,Hazrat Ata bin Yasar (Rahimahullah) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uski manind riwayat kartey hain. bayan kya ke koi logon par ameer ho to ( taqseem kartey huey ( kuch uskey hissey mein se le-ley aur kuch doosrey ke hissey mein se.
2785,Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba mein se eik shakhs ne Ubaidullah bin Salman se bayan kya ke jab hamne khaibar Fateh kya to logon ne apni apni ghaneematein nikalen. (yani ( saman aur qaidi aur unhen bechney lagey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padh kar farigh huey to eik aadmi aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool! maine aaj itna nafa hasil kya hai ke us wadi walon mein se kisi ko kya mila hoga. aapney farmaya : ''tu ne kya kama liya hai? '' usney kaha : main bechta raha aur khareedta raha yahan tak ke teen so auqiya ka nafa hasil kar liya hai. (eik auqiya chaalis dirham ka hota hai) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tumhen batata hun ke nafa kamaaney mein sab se afzal kon hai? ''usney puchha : wo kya hai aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney farmaya : ''do rakatein ( farz ( Namaz ke baad.''
2786,"bano Zubab ke eik shakhs zul-Joshan se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ehle-Badr se farigh ho gaey to main aap ki khidmat mein ghodey ka eik bachhda lekar hazir hua aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! main aap ke paas eik bachhda lekar aaya hun ye aap apney liye ley lijiye . aapney farmaya : ''mujhey iski zarurat nahin, lekin agar tum chaho to tumhen iskey badley Badr ki muntakhab zirhon mein se koi de-dun, to kar sakta hun.'' maine kaha : aaj to main uskey badley mein koi ghodi bhi nahin lunga. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''to phir mujhey bhi uski zarurat nahin hai.''"
2787,Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ne (apney eik khutbey mein) bayan kya : Amma baad. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi mushrik ki sohbat ikhtiyar karey aur uskey sath rihaaish rakhey to wo bhi usi ki tarah hai.''
